hobbies%20and%20interests.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiked%20you%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Tap%20this%20button%20to%20see%20any%20other%20users%20who%20have%20%26quot%3Bliked%26quot%3B%20your%20profile%2C%20and%20you%20can%20like%20or%20dismiss%20them%20from%20here%20as%20well.%20If%20you%20both%20choose%20Like%2C%20that%20person%20ends%20up%20in%20the%20Matches%20section.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMatches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20If%20both%20parties%20like%20each%20other%2C%20the%20other%20user%20will%20appear%20at%20the%20top%20of%20this%20page.%20Tap%20a%20photo%20to%20start%20a%20conversation%20with%20that%20person%2C%20and%20active%20conversations%20appear%20in%20the%20lower%20half%20of%20the%20page.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFriendship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20This%20section%20shows%20you%20more%20profiles%2C%20but%20the%20heart%20option%20for%20matching%20is%20replaced%20with%20a%20smiley-face%20icon%20that%20means%20you%20want%20to%20match%20as%20friends.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGear%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Customize%20whom%20you%20consider%20to%20be%20your%20ideal%20match.%20You%20can%20specify%20living%20distance%2C%20age%2C%20gender%2C%20height%2C%20language%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EMore%20to%20Explore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20section%2C%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20other%20options%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22876%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20shows%20More%20to%20Explore%20options%20of%20Facebook%20dating%20on%20mobile%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65133af651acc80019f0dc09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221232%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFacebook%20Dating%20gives%20you%20a%20lot%20of%20features%20unavailable%20in%20other%20dating%20apps%2C%20like%20the%20ability%20to%20see%20if%20an%20acquaintance%20also%20has%20a%20crush%20on%20you.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%20look%3C%2Fstr