3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0cf9357bff7001947ba20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-news-today-dow-worst-loss-march-economic-data-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Readings%20on%20sales%20of%20new%20homes%20and%20consumer%20confidence%20came%20in%20below%20forecasts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-news-today-dow-worst-loss-march-economic-data-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20long%20couples%20in%20lasting%20relationships%20should%20wait%20to%20start%20having%20sex%2C%20according%20to%20science%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221251%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22couple%20kissing%20wine%20love%20dating%20relationship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a8316c9d03072e6018b537e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22938%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20couples%20have%20to%20discuss%20when%20it's%20right%20for%20them%20to%20start%20having%20sex.%3Cp%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20new%20couples%2C%20moving%20too%20fast%20or%20too%20slow%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20getting%20physical%20can%20be%20a%20big%20worry.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20people%20wonder%20when%20the%20best%20time%20is%20to%20start%20being%20sexually%20intimate%20in%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20answer%20is%20complicated%2C%20spanning%20anywhere%20from%20a%20few%20dates%20to%20a%20few%20months%20after%20beginning%20to%20spend%20time%20together.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20all%20worried%20about%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20a%20relationship%2C%20thinking%20about%20whether%20we're%20moving%20too%20fast%20or%20slow%20with%20a%20potential%20mate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20got%20us%20wondering%3A%20When%20is%20the%20best%20time%20to%20start%20being%20sexually%20intimate%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20according%20to%20science%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20is%20complicated%2C%20spanning%20anywhere%20from%20a%20few%20dates%20to%20a%20few%20months%20after%20you%20start%20to%20spend%20time%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20it's%20hard%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20time%20in%20a%20relationship%20to%20have%20sex%20is%20because%20there%20hasn't%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20tackling%20that%20specific%20question.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20studies%20have%20looked%20at%20the%20health%20of%20a%20relationship%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20when%20couples%20first%20had%20sex%2C%20and%20the%20research%20that%20has%20been%20done%20mostly%20features%20specific%20samples%20of%20people%20%E2%80%94%20mainly%20college%20students%20or%20married%20heterosexual%20couples.FN%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221884%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20attracted%20to%20each%20other%20about%20to%20kiss%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6513346551acc80019f0da13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221413%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20researchers%20sai%20that%20sex%20should%20happen%20early%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20others%20said%20later.%3Cp%3EFG%20Trade%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EBut%20here's%20what%20we%20know%20about%20commitment%20and%20sex%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20may%20feel%20they%20need%20to%20reach%20milestones%2C%20like%20getting%20to%20know%20a%20person%20or%20sharing%20a%20first%20kiss%2C%20prior%20to%20having%20sex%20with%20a%20partner.%20But%20that's%20not%20the%20case%20for%20everyone%2C%20sex%20therapist%20Rachel%20Wright%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNone%20of%20these%20things%20are%20universal%20and%20every%20person%20is%20different.%20Some%20people%20need%20a%20safe%20emotional%20connection%20before%20having%20sex%2C%20some%20people%20don't%20need%20it%2C%20some%20want%20it%2C%20and%20some%20don't%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20because%20every%20relationship's%20sexual%20cadence%20is%20unique%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20predict%20how%20your%20first%20sexual%20experience%20with%20someone%20will%20pan%20out%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20being%20honest%20with%20yourself%20about%20your%20relationship%20goals%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20useful%20ways%20to%20decide%20when%20to%20have%20sex%2C%20according%20to%20Wright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20sex%20is%20important%20to%20you%2C%20do%20it%20when%20it%20feels%20good%20to%20do%20it.%20And%20understand%20that%20the%20more%20you%20know%20someone's%20body%2C%20mind%2C%20and%20preferences%2C%20the%20better%20the%20sex%20will%20often%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWright%20said%20that%20asking%20yourself%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20I%20want%20to%20have%20sex%20now%3F%20Is%20it%20societal%20conditioning%2C%20or%20because%20%3Cem%3EI%3C%2Fem%3E%20really%20want%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20could%20be%20a%20helpful%20question%20if%20you%20find%20yourself%20debating%20when%20to%20get%20intimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20emotional%20connection%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20any%20relationship%2C%20psychotherapist%20Toni%20Coleman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-should-you-have-sex-in-a-relationship-study-2015-7%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%20in%202015%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20you%20both%20agree%20not%20to%20push%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBe%20clear%20that%20the%20person%20is%20comfortable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20three%20different%20researchers%20have%20to%20say%20about%20when%20to%20have%20sex%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223399%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22honeymoon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651335281c099d0019ad1615%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222555%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20may%20take%20as%20little%20at%2036%20hours%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20be%20intimate%2C%20one%20scientist%20said.%3Cp%3EShutterstock%2F%20Tiffany%20Bryant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EOption%201%3A%20Give%20it%20a%20few%20weeks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20psychotherapist%20Barton%20Goldsmith%20a%20total%20of%203six%20hours%20spent%20together%20is%20all%20it%20takes%20to%20be%20ready.%20Those%20hours%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20consecutive%2C%20he%20previously%20told%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20it%20could%20be%20a%20dinner%20date%20plus%20a%20weekend%20afternoon%20spent%20together%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20until%20the%20hours%20add%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20people%2C%20that%20would%20probably%20take%20a%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20couple%20waits%20much%20longer%20than%20that%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20strong%20desire%20to%20have%20sex%20may%20begin%20to%20subside.%20While%20limited%2C%20there%20is%20data%20to%20back%20him%20up%20%E2%80%94%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F0092623X.2011.569637%23.VbkN2BNVhHw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%202012%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20heterosexual%20college%20students%20found%20that%20for%20each%20additional%20month%20of%20a%20relationship%2C%20women%20in%20relationships%20lost%20some%20sexual%20desire%2C%20but%20men%20did%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20more%20recent%20study%2C%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F27766993%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2017%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20followed%202%2C173%20Finnish%20women%20over%20seven%20years%20and%20found%20that%20those%20who%20stayed%20in%20the%20same%20relationship%20had%20a%20low%20sex%20drive%20compared%20to%20those%20who%20had%20new%20partners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOption%202%3A%20Hold%20off%20for%20a%20few%20months%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EColeman%20suggested%20that%20somewhere%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20of%20three%20months%20would%20be%20an%20ideal%20time%20to%20start%20being%20intimate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20should%20put%20you%20in%20a%20safer%20spot%20beyond%20the%20so-called%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwedding-therapist-says-honeymoon-phase-isnt-happiest-time-2021-11%5C%22%3E%20honeymoon%20phase%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20relationship%2C%20when%20your%20emotions%20have%20settled%20a%20bit%20and%20you're%20able%20to%20think%20more%20rationally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20match%20is%20somebody%20that%20makes%20you%20feel%20calm%20and%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20Talia%20Goldstein%2C%20a%20matchmaker%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fa-relationship-expert-reveals-the-3-signs-your-new-relationship-will-last-2016-6%231-you-dont-get-butterflies-when-you-think-about-the-other-person-1%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20honeymoon%20phase%20can%20be%20fun%2C%20it's%20full%20of%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20and%20can%20be%20emotionally%20volatile.%20Waiting%20until%20after%20that%20period%20can%20mean%20you're%20sure%20you've%20found%20a%20good%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20move%20past%20that%2C%20and%20your%20feet%20are%20more%20on%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Coleman%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20previous%20studies%20have%20said%20the%20couples%20who%20%26quot%3Bwaited%20until%20that%20level%20fared%20a%20lot%20better%20than%20people%20who%20had%20sex%20on%20the%20first%2C%20second%2C%20or%20third%20date.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldsmith%20disagrees%2C%20though%20%E2%80%94%20he%20thinks%20the%20time%20after%20the%20honeymoon%20period%20is%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20wid