%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftalent-insider%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%3ETalent%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20series%20containing%20expert%20advice%20to%20help%20business%20owners%20tackle%20a%20range%20of%20hiring%20challenges.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMastercard%20wants%20to%20be%20a%20firm%20where%20technologists%20are%20excited%20to%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20payments%20giant%20is%20actively%20hiring%20developers%20across%20its%20seven%20global%20technology%20hubs.%20To%20attract%20and%20retain%20top%20talent%2C%20the%20firm%20says%20it%20is%20taking%20steps%20to%20make%20its%20workplace%20and%20work%20culture%20a%20top%20destination%20for%20technologists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20first%20sense%20you%20get%20is%20that%20this%20is%20really%20a%20tech%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Oran%20Cummins%2C%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20APIs%20at%20Mastercard%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20the%20first%20impression%20that%20folks%20get.%20They're%20maybe%20a%20little%20surprised.%20They%20may%20think%20that%20they're%20walking%20into%20a%20traditional%20financial%20services%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22479%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oran%20Cummins%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649c985b6eb0a800194d8c91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22359%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOran%20Cummins%2C%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20APIs%20at%20Mastercard%3Cp%3EMastercard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EMastercard%20is%20best%20known%20as%20a%20card%20company%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20open%20banking%20push.%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insiderintelligence.com%2Finsights%2Fopen-banking-api-trends-explained%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpen%20banking%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20system%20where%20banks%20allow%20third%20parties%20to%20access%20financial%20consumer%20data%2C%20with%20the%20customer's%20consent%2C%20by%20opening%20up%20their%20application%20programming%20interfaces%2C%20or%20APIs.)%C2%A0%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20is%20hiring%20across%20technology%2C%20product%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20consulting%20fields.%20Within%20tech%2C%20the%20firm%20is%20adding%20software%20architects%2C%20product%20developers%20across%20IT%20and%20cybersecurity%2C%20projects%20and%20program%20managers%2C%20and%20talent%20in%20crypto%2C%20artificial-intelligence%20strategy%2C%20and%20RiskRecon%2C%20a%20risk%20management%20startup%20that%20Mastercard%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2019%2F12%2F23%2Fmastercard-acquires-security-assessment-startup-riskrecon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacquired%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opportunity%20to%20innovate%20on%20projects%20and%20code%20that%20will%20%26quot%3Bship%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20or%20go%20live%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20major%20incentive%20for%20technologists%20joining%20the%20firm%2C%20according%20to%20Cummins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20saying%20at%20Mastercard%3A%20If%20it%20doesn't%20scale%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20wants%20to%20work%20on%20software%20that%20nobody%20uses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20Mastercard's%20open%20banking%20business%2C%20production%20code%20may%20be%20released%20multiple%20times%20a%20day.%20Other%20projects%2C%20like%20those%20that%20will%20scale%20to%20a%20global%20level%2C%20may%20take%20months%20of%20development%20and%20planning%20before%20they%20roll%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20perk%3A%20Developers%20get%20'autonomy%20days'%20to%20work%20on%20pet%20projects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20are%20given%20time%20to%20work%20on%20their%20work-related%20pet%20projects%2C%20too.%20These%20are%20called%20%26quot%3Bautonomy%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20developer%20used%20an%20autonomy%20day%20to%20create%20a%20program%20that%20automatically%20sorts%20and%20categorizes%20customer%20support%20emails.%20Another%20developed%20a%20%26quot%3Bdark%20mode%26quot%3B%20setting%20for%20Mastercard's%20internal%2C%20back-end%20software%20interface%20to%20reduce%20eye%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20still%20gets%20a%20lot%20of%20kudos%20for%20that%2C%20Cummins%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technologists%20Mastercard%20wants%20to%20hire%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bmultiplier%20effect%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20they%20can%20do%2C%20what%20they%20can%20deliver%2C%20and%20how%20they%20can%20raise%20the%20bar%20within%20the%20organization%2C%20according%20to%20Cummins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20what%20they're%20able%20to%20build.%20It's%20the%20way%20in%20which%20they%20build%20it%20with%20future%20extension%20in%20mind.%20It's%20built%20with%20flexibility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20you%20create%20well-designed%20software%2C%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20move%20fast.%20It%20allows%20you%20to%20very%20quickly%20diversify%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20qualifications%20and%20responsibilities%20listed%20on%20Mastercard%20tech%20job%20postings%20are%20intentionally%20vague%20so%20as%20to%20attract%20a%20diverse%20pool%20of%20talent%20with%20broad%20skill%20sets%2C%20Cummins%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20is%20a%20leading%20channel%20for%20recruitment%2C%20but%20the%20firm%20also%20sources%20from%20other%20sites%20like%20Handshake%20(a%20job%20board%20designed%20for%20college%20students)%2C%20Built%20In%20(a%20tech%20job%20board)%2C%20and%20ColorStack%20(a%20job%20board%20designed%20for%20Black%20and%20Latinx%20computer%20science%20students).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20salary%20range%20for%20a%20lead%20software%20engineer%20based%20in%20New%20York%20is%20%24158%2C000%20to%20%24245%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20an%20earlier%20job%20posting%20on%20the%20Mastercard%20careers%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20from%20the%20seven%20tech%20hubs%20located%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20including%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Dublin%2C%20Sydney%2C%20and%20Vancouver.%20The%20hubs%20are%20Mastercard's%20centers%20of%20innovation%20and%20collaboration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mastercard's%20New%20York%20City%20Tech%20Hub%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649c9b09ec2dd400195fd85b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22948%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20Mastercard's%20New%20York%20City%20Tech%20Hub%2C%20featuring%20the%20coffee%20bar%20in%20the%20background.%3Cp%3EMastercard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20City%20Tech%20Hub%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20a%20modern%2C%20multi-level%20office%20located%20on%205th%20Avenue%20in%20the%20Flatiron%20District.%20The%20walls%20are%20covered%20in%20live%20moss%20and%20greenery.%20Floor-to-ceiling%20windows%20give%20a%20view%20of%20the%20city%20skyline.%20And%20employees%20have%20access%20to%20the%20rooftop%20and%20balconies%20as%20well%20as%20portable%20chargers%20to%20enable%20mobility%20within%20the%20office.%20There's%20even%20a%20for-purchase%20coffee%20bar%20with%20a%20barista.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20have%20the%20option%20to%20work%20remote%2C%20hybrid%2C%20or%20in-person.%20They%20can%20also%20work%20remotely%20from%20anywhere%20for%20up%20to%20four%20weeks%20per%20year%20with%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcareers.mastercard.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fblogarticle%2Fhow-mastercard-employees-are-using-their-work-from-elsewhere-benefit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWork%20from