%2C%20and%20then%20go%20all-in%20on%20their%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20holds%20us%20back%20from%20fully%20committing%20to%20our%20purpose%20are%20these%20metaphorical%20boats%20that%20tell%20us%20to%20retreat%2C%26quot%3B%20Higgins%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20leave%20a%20door%20open%20for%20retreat%2C%20it%20undermines%20your%20resolve.%20You%20need%20the%20pain%20of%20potential%20failure%20to%20drive%20you%20to%20take%20extraordinary%20acts%20to%20succeed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScared%3F%20That's%20the%20point%2C%20according%C2%A0to%20Higgins.%20It's%20that%20kind%20of%20productive%20anxiety%20that%20drives%20entrepreneurs.%20Without%20risk%2C%20he%20said%2C%20reward%20is%20more%20elusive.%20Even%20flourishing%20founders%20will%20find%20ways%20to%20continuously%20access%20pools%20of%20doubt%20or%20fear%20that%20drive%20them%20forward%20toward%20the%20next%20thing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Higgins%2C%20there%20was%20no%20plan%20B.%20The%20cofounder%20of%20RSE%20Ventures%20and%20investor%20in%20such%20brands%20as%20Momofuku%2C%20VaynerMedia%2C%20and%20Magnolia%20Bakery%2C%20he%20grew%20up%20poor%C2%A0in%20Queens%2C%20New%20York%2C%20the%20youngest%20child%20of%20a%20single%20mother%20with%20depression%20and%20other%20health%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiggins%20started%20working%20at%20age%2010%2C%20then%20dropped%20out%20of%20school%20at%2016%20so%20he%20could%20get%20his%20GED%20and%20attend%20college%20%E2%80%94%20and%20start%20earning%20real%20money%20%E2%80%93%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%20His%20mother%20died%20just%20as%20his%20career%20began%20to%20take%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%2C%20Higgins%20worked%20in%20communications%20for%20dotcom-era%20grocery%20startup%20Kozmo.com.%20He%20was%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Rudolph%20Giuliani's%20press%20secretary%20on%209%2F11%2C%20and%20later%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20Lower%20Manhattan%20Development%20Corporation.%20RSE%20Ventures%20was%20founded%20in%202012%2C%20and%20Higgins%20also%20held%20executive%20roles%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Jets%20and%20Miami%20Dolphins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMoving%20from%20side%20hustle%20to%20startup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20resume%20looks%20like%20nonstop%20progression%2C%20Higgins%20shares%20in%20the%20book%20the%20tradeoffs%20involved%2C%20such%20as%20when%20he%20decided%20to%C2%A0%20leave%20a%20%26quot%3Bdream%20job%26quot%3B%20as%20an%20operations%20executive%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Book%20Jacket%20for%20Burn%20the%20Boats%20by%20Matt%20Higgins%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6510c7cee2c0220019ef35b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERSE%20Ventures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20I%20wasn't%20using%20all%20my%20skills.%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20a%20place%20of%20perpetual%20growth%20and%20disruption%2C%20not%20presiding%20over%20things%20that%20were%20generally%20fine.%20So%20I%20quit.%20Crazy%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20decision%20would%20lead%20to%20his%20connecting%20with%20real%20estate%20developer%20Stephen%20Ross%2C%20owner%20of%20the%20Miami%20Dolphins%20and%20later%20Higgins'%20cofounder%20of%20RSE%20Ventures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20working%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20it's%20tough%20to%20know%20when%20the%20time%20might%20be%20right%20to%20quit%20your%20day%20job.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20are%20in%20the%20land%20of%20the%20side%20hustle%2C%20you're%20trying%20to%20identify%20that%20which%20would%20be%20fulfilling%20enough%2C%20rewarding%20enough%2C%20and%20sustaining%20enough%20to%20be%20your%20plan%20A%2C%26quot%3B%20Higgins%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20financial%20guarantees%20from%20day%20one%2C%20however%2C%20that's%20the%20wrong%20goal.%20%26quot%3BIf%20that's%20your%20framework%2C%20you'll%20never%20go%20all%20the%20way%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20The%20trick%20is%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20is%20the%20level%20of%20risk%20you%20can%20tolerate%2C%20but%20not%20eliminate%20it%20completely.%20Otherwise%2C%20he%20said%2C%20you%20are%20in%20danger%20of%20losing%20focus%20on%20the%20best%20possible%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOptimizing%20anxiety%20while%20avoiding%20burnout%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHiggins%20dedicates%20an%20entire%20chapter%20to%20optimizing%20anxiety%2C%20including%20tools%20for%20letting%20it%20spiral%20out%20of%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnxiety%20is%20a%20power%20source%2C%26quot%3B%20Higgins%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BLike%20nuclear%20power%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20unleashed%20the%20same%20time%20it's%20contained%20or%20you%20have%20a%20total%20meltdown.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurnout%20is%20common%20for%20anyone%20pursuing%20their%20passion.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20cost%20to%20being%20all-in%20because%20the%20stakes%20are%20always%20very%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20it's%20propelling%20you%20to%20greatness%2C%20it%20does%20grind%20you%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20advises%20identifying%20the%20specific%20parts%20of%20your%20life%20that%20are%20essential%20to%20your%20well-being%2C%20and%20protecting%20them%20%E2%80%94%20but%20defining%20them%20narrowly%20so%20that%20you're%20not%20adding%20stress%20by%20worrying%20about%20things%20that%20ultimately%20don't%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiggins%20also%20tries%20to%20meditate%20every%20day%2C%20citing%20examples%20of%20other%20leaders%20from%20Ray%20Dalio%20to%20Bill%20Gates%20who%20swear%20by%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMainly%20though%2C%20you%20have%20to%20learn%20to%20let%20go%20when%20things%20don't%20go%20your%20way.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20what%20you%20can%2C%20forgive%20yourself%20when%20you%20don't%20achieve%20perfection%2C%20and%20keep%20trying.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburn-the-boats-matt-higgins-entrepreneurs-ditch-plan-b-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695756849000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511e1c7e2c0220019ef5ae1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburn-the-boats-matt-higgins-entrepreneurs-ditch-plan-b-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Matt%20Higgins%2C%20cofounder%20of%20RSE%20Ventures%20and%20guest%20shark%20on%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20written%20a%20book%20called%20%26quot%3BBurn%20the%20Boats%26quot%3B%20with%20advice%20for%20entrepreneurs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhood%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Hood)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburn-the-boats-matt-higgins-entrepreneurs-ditch-plan-b-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2221%20British%20MPs%20call%20on%20UK%20to%20halt%20FTA%20negotiations%20with%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695756797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103970720%2Cimgsize-48868.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2F21-british-mps-call-on-uk-to-halt-fta-negotiations-with-india-whilst-manipur-violence-continues%2Farticleshow%2F103970663.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22NAOMI%20CANTON%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2F21-british-mps-call-on-uk-to-halt-fta-negotiations-with-india-whilst-manipur-violence-continues%2Farticleshow%2F103970663.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20tells%20a%20gun%20store%20he%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20buy%20a%20Glock%2C%20raising%20lega