eapons%20and%20drugs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20Mr%20Mann%20to%20flag%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20smuggling%20of%20weapons%20from%20within%20the%20country.%20Pointing%20out%20that%20this%20is%20posing%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20threat%26quot%3B%20to%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20number%20of%20weapons%20smuggled%20from%20within%20the%20country%20(especially%20from%20states%20like%20Madhya%20Pradesh)%20is%20much%20more%20than%20is%20smuggled%20from%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdvocating%20for%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20regional%20centre%20of%20National%20Security%20Guards%20(NSG)%20in%20Pathankot%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20Punjab%20is%20always%20prone%20to%20terror%20attacks%20from%20across%20the%20border.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20NSG%20hub%2C%20which%20was%20announced%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20must%20be%20set%20up%20at%20the%20earliest%20to%20help%20safeguard%20the%20country's%20borders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20also%20underscored%20the%20need%20for%20revision%20of%20the%20clause%20of%20having%20to%20pay%20for%20paramilitary%20forces%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20when%20needed.%20He%20said%20that%20this%20clause%20of%20'paramilitary%20forces%20on%20rent'%20should%20be%20abolished%20as%20far%20as%20Punjab%20is%20concerned%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20centre%20must%20be%20magnanimous%20in%20allocation%20as%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20also%20spoke%20on%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20genuine%20federal%20structure%20in%20the%20country%20and%20said%20that%20the%20need%20for%20more%20financial%20arid%20political%20power%20to%20states%20has%20been%20felt%20across%20the%20spectrum%20of%20political%20opinion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20wide%20consensus%2C%20cutting%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20that%20the%20state%20governments%20need%20to%20be%20giv