20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20it%20would%20be%20correct%20to%20assume%20that%20he%20is%20referring%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeven%20though%20he%20has%20repeatedly%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20double%20standards%20in%20fighting%20terrorism%20several%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Canada%20expelled%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20India%20did%20the%20same%20to%20a%20Canadian%20official%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20measure.%20India%20has%20also%20suspended%20visa%20operations%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%20and%20asked%20the%20Canadian%20high%20commission%20to%20downsize.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20through%20its%20spokesperson%2C%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20given%20two%20press%20releases%20and%20one%20briefing%20that%20dealt%20with%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%20India%20had%20dismissed%20the%20accusations%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20main%20issue%20was%20that%20Canada%20had%20refused%20to%20take%20action%20to%20stop%20the%20activities%20of%20Khalistani%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20all%20the%20foreign%20ministers%20of%20the%20five-eyes%20countries%20have%20spoken%20publicly%20over%20the%20past%20week%2C%20indicating%20that%20India%20should%20join%20the%20investigation%20and%20called%20for%20accountability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20asserted%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctransnational%20repression%E2%80%9D%20was%20unacceptable%2C%20highlighting%20that%20Washington%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccollaborating%E2%80%9D%20with%20Canada.%20Australian%20foreign%20minister%20Penny%20Wong%20said%20that%20she%20had%20raised%20the%20%E2%80%9Cserious%E2%80%9D%20allegations%20with%20the%20Indian%20side.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20US%20and%20Australia%20have%20repeatedly%20asked%20India%20to%20join%20the%20investigation.%20The%20MEA%20spokesperson%20had%20pointed%20out%20India%20was%20willing%20to%20look%20at%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20information%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20that%20nothing%20had%20been%20shared%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUK%20foreign%20secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20carefully%20phrased%20his%20concerns%2C%20but%20acknowledged%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20allegations.%20Even%20the%20smallest%20member%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20alliance%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20had%20its%20foreign%20minister%20Nanaia%20Mahuta%20express%20her%20unease.%20She%20stated%20that%20if%20the%20reports%20proved%20accurate%2C%20it%20would%20raise%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20concerns%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20UNGA%20plenary%2C%20their%20Indian%20counterpart%2C%20Jaishankar%2C%20had%20not%20made%20any%20statement%2C%20even%20indirectly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20noted%2C%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20silence%20for%20a%20week%20during%20the%20latest%20diplomatic%20crisis%20was%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20striking%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esince%20he%20is%20known%20for%20robustly%20defending%20against%20foreign%20criticism%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20all%20his%20counterparts%20had%20made%20public%20remarks%20urging%20India%20to%20take%20the%20allegations%20seriously.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-indias-diplomatic-standoff-with-canada-jaishankars-silence-stands-out%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20pointed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20out%20that%20Jaishankar%20would%20have%20two%20opportunities%20to%20address%20the%20questions%20%E2%80%93%20one%20during%20the%20UNGA%20plenary%20and%20again%20when%20he%20goes%20to%20Washington%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20envoy%20to%20Canada%20has%20already%20stated%20that%20input%20from%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20countries%20had%20informed%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20made%20in%20parliament%20on%20September%2018.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20public%20response%20from%20India%20to%20the%20remarks%20by%20the%20US%20envoy%20to%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20the%20Canadian%20permanent%20representative%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20Bob%20Rae%20also%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20diplomatic%20fracas%20with%20India%20by%20name.%20However%2C%20he%20pointedly%20noted%20that%20one%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20bend%20the%20rules%20of%20state-to-state%20relations%20for%20political%20expediency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20the%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cuphold%20the%20values%20of%20free%20and%20democratic%20societies%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20asserted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20bend%20the%20rules%20of%20state-to-state%20relations%20for%20political%20expediency%2C%20because%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20and%20continue%20to%20see%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20democracies%20are%20under%20threat%20through%20various%20means%20of%20foreign%20interference%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Jaishankar%20spoke%20that%20response%20to%20terrorism%20cannot%20be%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20convenience%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Canadian%20diplomat%20said%20that%20rules%20for%20relations%20between%20countries%20cannot%20be%20subverted%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20expediency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20while%20Rae%20said%20that%20the%20international%20rules-based%20system%20was%20under%20threat%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20norms%20are%20still%20being%20shaped%20by%20a%20small%20club%20and%20the%20rules%20applied%20unevenly%20across%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%20is%2C%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20adhere%20to%20the%20rules%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20agreed%20to%2C%20the%20very%20fabric%20of%20our%20open%20and%20free%20societies%20may%20tear%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20speech%2C%20Jaishankar%20praised%20India%E2%80%99s%20advocacy%20for%20concerns%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20especially%20as%20chair%20of%20the%20G-20%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20not%20mentioning%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20world%20is%20witnessing%20an%20exceptional%20period%20of%20turmoil.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20it%20is%2C%20structural%20inequities%20and%20uneven%20development%20have%20imposed%20burdens%20on%20the%20Global%20South.%20But%20stresses%20have%20been%20aggravated%20by%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20the%20repercussions%20of%20ongoing%20conflicts%2C%20tensions%20and%20disputes.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20socio-economic%20gains%20of%20recent%20years%20have%20been%20rolled%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20G-20%20summit%20resulted%20in%20a%20declaration%20despite%20geo-political%20divisions.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20East-West%20polarisation%20is%20so%20sharp%20and%20North-South%20divide%20so%20deep%2C%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Summit%20also%20affirms%20that%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue%20are%20the%20only%20effective%20solutions.%20The%20international%20order%20is%20diverse%20and%20we%20must%20cater%20for%20divergences%2C%20if%20not%20differences.%20The%20days%20when%20a%20few%20nations%20set%20the%20agenda%20and%20expected%20others%20to%20fall%20in%20line%20are%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695752138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26233257%2FScreenshot-2023-09-26-at-11.31.05-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fjab-west-jaishankar-political-convenience-response-terrorism-canada%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20plenary%2C%20the%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said%20that%20response%20to%20terrorism%20cannot%20be%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20convenience%E2%80%9D.%20Canadian's%20permanent%20representative%20to%20the%20UN%20Bob%20Rae%20said%20that%20rules%20for%20relations%20between%20countries%20cannot%20be%20subverted%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20expediency%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fjab-west-jaishankar-political-convenience-response-terrorism-canada%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22London's%20Gatwick%20Airport%20Limits%20Flights%20Due%20To%20Covid-19%20Outbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGatwick%20Airport%2C%20London's%20second-busiest%2C%20has%20canceled%20several%20flights%20because%20of%20staff%20shortages%20in%20air%20traffic%20control%20blamed%20on%20the%20Covid-19%20outbreak%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F09%2F26%2Fcovid-chaos-gatwick-britain-airport-cancel-flights-air-traffic-control-nats%2F%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20More%20than%2040%20flights%20were%20canceled%20over%20the%20weekend.%20The%20airport%20has%20also%20moved%20to%20limit%20the%20number%20of%20planes%20coming%20and%20going%20from%20its%20runway%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20week%2C%20the%20airport's%20CEO%20Stewart%20Wingate%C2%A0said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20airport%20said%20a%20daily%20800-flight%20limit%2C%20including%20both%20departures%20and%20arrivals%2C%20has%20been%20imposed%20until%20Sunday.%20The%20daily%20cap%20will%20prevent%20last-minute%20cancellations%20and%20delays%20for%20passengers%20while%20National%20Air%20Traffic%20Services%20(NATS)%20gets%20back%20to%20normal%2C%20the%20airport%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20number%20of%20cancellations%20will%20be%20on