Cspan%3E%20published%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwill-the-un-high-level-meeting-address-indias-problem-of-tb-drugs-stock-out-situation%5C%22%3Epiece%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20September%2022%2C%202023%2C%20that%20cited%20family%20members%20of%20TB%20patients%20and%20people%20working%20to%20manage%20the%20disease%20in%20six%20states%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20acute%20shortage%20of%20drugs%20had%20hit%20patients%20suffering%20from%20drug-resistant%20TB%20very%20hard.%20The%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20TB%20programme%20head%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20UN%20agency%20was%20aware%20of%20and%20concerned%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20India.%20Two%20doctors%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20also%20expressed%20concern%20%E2%80%93%20saying%20the%20shortage%20could%20have%20irreversible%20consequences%20for%20patients.%20The%20Union%20health%20ministry%20had%20not%20replied%20to%20the%20queries%20sent%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwill-the-un-high-level-meeting-address-indias-problem-of-tb-drugs-stock-out-situation%5C%22%3EUnprecedented%20TB%20Drugs%20Stock-Out%20in%20India%3A%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20Skips%20UN%20High-Level%20Meet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20denial%2C%20a%20joint%20statement%20from%20five%20civil%20society%20groups%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20TB%20community%20in%20India%20consisting%20of%20TB%20survivors%2C%20TB%20Advocates%2C%20CCM%20members%20representing%20the%20TB%20affected%20community%2C%20Clinicians%20treating%20TB%20Patients%20and%20TB%20Champions%20are%20very%20concerned%20with%20the%20notice%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20(MoHFW)today%20saying%20that%20the%20TB%20Drugs%20stock%20out%20situation%20is%20a%20myth%20and%20a%20media%20hype.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20organisations%20said%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cup%20until%20today%E2%80%9D%20inundated%20with%20%E2%80%9Cdistressing%20appeals%20from%20patients%2C%20relatives%20and%20doctors%20alike%20who%20are%20grappling%20with%20difficulties%20in%20obtaining%20TB%20medications%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20was%20endorsed%20by%20TB%20Mukth%20Vahini%20%5BBihar%5D%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EARK%20Foundation%20%5BNagaland%5D%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobal%20Coalition%20of%20TB%20Advocates%2C%20a%20global%20body%20of%20civil%20society%20groups%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERainbow%20TB%20Forum%20%5BTamil%20Nadu%5D%3B%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETouched%20by%20TB%2C%20a%20national%20coalition%20of%20people%20affected%20by%20TB%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%20released%20information%20about%20stocks%20of%20various%20drugs%20available%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20would%20last%20six%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20calculation%20done%20by%20a%20civil%20society%20group%20member%2C%20Vaishnavi%20Jayakumar%2C%20using%20the%20data%20from%20the%20tenders%20available%20online%2C%20shows%20that%20one%20drug%20is%20available%20just%20for%20a%20month%2C%20another%20one%20for%20less%20than%20one%20month%2C%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth.%20Jayakumar%20looked%20at%20the%20tenders%20to%20understand%20the%20yearly%20requirement%20of%20these%20drugs%20and%20thus%20deduced%20the%20monthly%20requirement.%20The%20tenders%20are%20available%20on%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Central%20Medical%20Services%20Society%20(CMSS)%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmss.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20CMSS%2