ce%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20regulatory%20actions%20by%20US%20authorities.%20The%20exchange%20has%20laid%20off%20a%20total%20of%201%2C500%20workers%20over%20the%20past%20three%20months%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20slash%20expenses%20and%20prepare%20for%20a%20slump%20in%20business.%20Over%20a%20dozen%20senior%20executives%20have%20left%20the%20company%20during%20that%20time%2C%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ffinance%2Fcurrencies%2Fthe-worlds-biggest-crypto-firm-is-melting-down-338b8e17%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaiko%2C%20a%20source%20of%20cryptocurrency%20market%20data%2C%20reports%20that%2C%20down%20from%20about%2070%20per%20cent%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20Binance%20currently%20handles%20about%20half%20of%20cryptocurrency%20exchanges%20involving%20direct%20purchases%20and%20sales.%20Due%20to%20its%20huge%20size%2C%20Binance's%20future%20has%20significant%20ramifications%20for%20the%20cryptocurrency%20sector.%20While%20experts%20in%20the%20field%20believe%20that%20other%20exchanges%20might%20step%20in%20to%20take%20Binance's%20place%20if%20it%20collapses%2C%20there%20is%20concern%20that%2C%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20market%20liquidity%20may%20disappear%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20significant%20decrease%20in%20token%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20institutional%20trader%20revealed%20to%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20that%20their%20business%20had%20prepared%20backup%20plans%20to%20quickly%20withdraw%20funds%20from%20Binance%20in%20the%20case%20of%20an%20emergency.%20The%20co-founder%20and%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20of%20Binance%2C%20Yi%20He%2C%20highlighted%20his%20commitment%20to%20overcome%20these%20difficulties%20in%20a%20message%20to%20the%20company's%20workers%20last%20month.%20He%20emphasised%20that%20every%20struggle%20is%20a%20make-or-break%20moment%20and%20that%20the%20only%20real%20threat%20is%20one's%20own%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBinance%20has%20a%20history%20of%20investing%20outside%20cryptocurrency%20initiatives%2C%20such%20as%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter).%20Binance's%20co-founder%20Changpeng%20Zhao%2C%20often%20known%20as%20CZ%2C%20is%20a%20well-known%20figure%20in%20the%20cryptocurrency%20community%20and%20has%208.6%20million%20X%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELong-running%20investigation%20by%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20might%20result%20in%20Binance%20and%20Zhao%20being%20charged%20with%20crimes%20and%20paying%20hefty%20fines.%20The%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20(SEC)%20is%20suing%20Binance%20as%20well%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20engaged%20in%20illegal%20activities%20in%20the%20US%20and%20misappropriated%20consumer%20funds.%20The%20business%20claims%20that%20consumer%20money%20is%20safe%20and%20that%20it%20is%20committed%20to%20compliance%20even%20if%20it%20acknowledges%20prior%20errors%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20global%20presence%2C%20Binance's%20accessibility%20has%20been%20restricted%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20including%20Europe%2C%20where%20more%20nations%20are%20banning%20its%20operations.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20Binance%20has%20witnessed%20a%20sharp%20fall%20in%20activity%2C%20with%20the%20recent%20departure%20of%20its%20CEO%2C%20legal%20chief%2C%20and%20risk%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695750180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-07%2F1375vtro_binance_625x300_30_July_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbinances-hegemony-shakes-as-us-regulatory-threat-looms-report-4426752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Long-running%20investigation%20by%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20might%20result%20in%20Binance%20and%20its%20CEO%20being%20charged%20with%20crimes%20and%20paying%20hefty%20fines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbinances-hegemony-shakes-as-us-regulatory-threat-looms-report-4426752%