ivities%E2%80%9D%20through%20various%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20electronic%20devices%2C%20because%20of%20which%20the%20government%20was%20%E2%80%93%20with%20immediate%20effect%20%E2%80%93%20suspending%20the%20Internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20says%20that%20the%20Internet%20was%20facilitating%20bulk%20SMSes%20and%20mobilisation%20of%20mobs%20of%20agitators%20and%20demonstrators%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20may%20cause%20loss%20of%20life%20and%2For%20damage%20to%20public%2Fprivate%20property%E2%80%9D%20or%20aggravate%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20It%20adds%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20Government%20has%20decided%20to%20suspend%2Fcurb%20mobile%20internet%20data%20services%2C%20as%20well%20as%20internet%2Fdata%20services%20through%20VPN%2C%20in%20the%20territorial%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Manipur%20for%20five%20(5)%20days%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%20until%207%3A45%20PM%20on%2001-10-2023%E2%80%A6.%20and%20the%20same%20will%20be%20reviewed%20before%20the%20expiry%20of%20the%20orders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20internet%20shutdown%20in%20Manipur.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20Internet%20was%20severed%20143%20days%20%E2%80%93%20from%20May%203%2C%20when%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%20began%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Finternet-ban-in-manipur-to-be-lifted-today-says-cm-biren-singh%5C%22%3Euntil%20September%2023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20second%20shutdown%20has%20commenced%20again%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-internet-shutdowns-hurt-its-vulnerable-communities-digital-india%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Trigger-Happy%20Internet%20Shutdowns%20Hurt%20its%20Poor%20and%20Marginalised%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20comes%20amid%20protests%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22ht