22%26quot%3BNo%20Merger%20Until%20Air%20India%20Gets%20To%20Level%20Of%20Vistara%26quot%3B%3A%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20and%20the%20Centre%20are%20aligned%20on%20making%20India%20a%20civil%20aviation%20hub%2C%20like%20Dubai%20or%20Singapore%2C%20and%20this%20is%20part%20of%20the%20company's%20plan%20as%20well%2C%20the%20airline's%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20and%20Managing%20Director%20Campbell%20Wilson%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Wilson%20spoke%20on%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20and%20said%20he%20is%20upbeat%20not%20just%20about%20the%20direction%20that%20the%20company%20is%20going%20in%20but%20also%20what%20the%20future%20holds%20for%20Indian%20aviation.%20He%20also%20discussed%20safety%2C%20the%20airline's%20new%20aircraft%2C%20the%20timeline%20for%20the%20Air%20India-Vistara%20merger%2C%20and%20the%20battle%20with%20IndiGo%2C%20which%20is%20the%20other%20behemoth%20in%20Indian%20aviation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Effort%20Spared%20on%20Safety%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20part%20of%20the%20government%20for%20a%20long%20time%20has%20instilled%20a%20certain%20culture%20in%20Air%20India%20and%20that%20is%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20that%20the%20civil%20aviation%20regulator%20had%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20carrier%20over%20safety%20issues%2C%20Mr%20Wilson%20said.%20He%20was%20answering%20a%20question%20on%20the%20recent%20suspension%20of%20the%20airline's%20Chief%20of%20Flight%20Safety%20for%20a%20month%20after%20an%20inspection%20found%20lapses%20in%20the%20carrier's%20accident-prevention%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20reasons%20why%20Air%20India%20is%20what%20it%20is.%20It's%20had%20a%20long%20history%2C%20background%20as%20part%20of%20the%20government.%20That's%20imbued%20a%20certain%20culture.%20And%20we%20are%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20bringing%20in%20people%2C%20bringing%20in%20training%2C%20bringing%20in%20systems%2C%20bringing%20in%20consequence%20management%2C%20and%20really%20demonstrating%20what%20world-class%20standards%20are%20in%20a%20safety%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20sad%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MD%20emphasised%20that%20they%20are%20actively%20%26quot%3Bplugging%20into%26quot%3B%20external%20bodies%2C%20like%20the%20International%20Air%20Transport%20Association%20and%20the%20Association%20of%20Asia%20Pacific%20Airlines%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20airline%20deeply%20understands%20the%20standards%20that%20are%20required.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPromulgating%20them%20through%20an%20organisation%20that%20has%20been%20acting%20in%20a%20certain%20way%20for%20a%20long%20time%20takes%20time.%20And%20educating%20people%20and%20reinforcing%20that%20standards%20that%20might%20have%20been%20acceptable%20in%20the%20past%20are%20no%20longer%20acceptable%20now%20requires%20constant%20attention.%20We're%20not%20sparing%20any%20effort%20in%20making%20this%20happen.%20It%20is%20disappointing%20that%20we%20have%20these%20episodes%2C%20but%20they%20have%20to%20be%20episodes%20that%20we%20learn%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAviation%20Hub%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Civil%20Aviation%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20had%20said%20that%20India%20could%20not%20only%20become%20an%20aviation%20hub%20like%20Dubai%2C%20Doha%20or%20Singapore%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%20or%20less%2C%20but%20it%20could%20also%20have%20multiple%20hubs%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20Delhi%20airport%2C%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Wilson%20was%20asked%20for%20his%20thoughts%20on%20this%2C%20and%20whether%20India%20could%20see%20people%20flying%20into%20Delhi%20on%20their%20way%20to%20other%20places%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20doing%20so%20from%20Qatar%20or%20Dubai%2C%20Mr%20Wilson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20not%20binary%2C%20you%20either%20don't%20or%20you%20do.%20Air%20India%20already%20carries%20people%20from%20Europe%20into%20Delhi%20and%20they%20connect%20onwards%20to%20Asia%20or%20Australasia.%20As%20a%20proportion%20of%20our%20total%20traffic%2C%20it's%20relatively%20small%2C%20but%20as%20we%20expand%20our%20frequency%2C%20as%20we%20improve%20our%20product%2C%20as%20the%20transit%20experience%20in%20Delhi%20improves%2C%20that%20will%20just%20get%20increasingly%20more.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20all%20really%20is%20a%20hub.%20Now%2C%20will%20it%20become%20the%20mega%20hub%20of%20the%20likes%20of%20others%3F%20In%20terms%20of%20volume%20of%20people%2C%20absolutely%20yes.%20But%20the%20structure%20will%20change%20because%20India%20has%20such%20a%20huge%20point-to-point%20demand%2C%20whether%20from%20city%20or%20whether%20from%20country%20going%20to%20somewhere%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20MD%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20international%20component%20of%20India's%20hub%20is%20almost%20certainly%20going%20to%20be%20smaller%20than%20it%20would%20be%20in%20a%20city-state%2C%20which%20doesn't%20have%20the%20supporting%20population%20that%20the%20country%20enjoys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20absolutely%2C%20we%20should%20have%20hubs%2C%20larger%20hubs%20in%20India.%20They%20can%20and%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20should%20be%20more%20than%20one.%20It%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Air%20India's%20future%20plan.%20And%20so%20we're%20fully%20aligned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMerger%20With%20Vistara%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20needs%20to%20get%20to%20the%20level%20of%20Vistara%2C%20which%20was%20built%20on%20the%20latest%20technology%20and%20had%20new%20aircraft%2C%20before%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20airlines%20can%20happen%2C%20Mr%20Wilson%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20new%20carrier%20will%20probably%20retain%20the%20'Air%20India'%20name%2C%20which%20comes%20with%20a%2091-year%20heritage%20and%20is%20known%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20said%20that%20the%20future%20airline%20will%20probably%20be%20called%20Air%20India.%20But%20we%20won't%20be%20merging%20Vistara%20and%20Air%20India%20until%20such%20time%20that%20we%20feel%20that%20Air%20India%20has%20reached%20the%20level%20that%20Vistara%20is%20at.%20With%20Vistara%20as%20part%20of%20the%20family%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20we%20can%20learn%20from...%20I%20think%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20that%20Vistara%20has%20been%20successful%20is%20a%20very%20young%20airline%20that%20was%20built%20on%20latest%20technology%2C%20had%20new%20aircraft.%20And%20these%20are%20things%20that%20Air%20India%20will%20have%20in%20due%20course%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Air%20India%20MD%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20inevitable%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20and%20we%20will%20not%20stop%20until%20Air%20India%20reaches%20at%20least%20Vistara's%20level.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Air%20India%20carries%20the%20name%20'Air%20India'%2C%20which%20is%20known%20and%20beloved%20around%20the%20world.%20And%20it%20has%2091%20years%20of%20history%20and%20heritage%20and%20recognition.%20So%20I%20think%20logically%2C%20internationally%2C%20Air%20India%20is%20by%20far%20the%20better%20name%20to%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndiGo%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20IndiGo%20and%20the%20challenges%20of%20competing%20with%20a%20low-cost%20airline%2C%20which%20is%20now%20making%20a%20significant%20foray%20into%20the%20international%20market%20as%20well%2C%20the%20Air%20India%20MD%20said%20both%20carriers%20are%20addressing%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20different%20market%20segments%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20evidenced%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20Australia%20you%20have%20a%20full-service%20and%20a%20low-cost%20airline.%20In%20Singapore%2C%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20you%20can%20sort%20of%20take%20your%20pick.%20We%20will%20stand%20for%20full%20service%20at%20Air%20India.%20Product%20quality%2C%20consistency%2C%20warmth%20of%20service%2C%20full%20service%2C%20meals%2C%20entertainment%2C%20comfortable%20seats%2C%20business%20class%2C%20first%20class%2C%20premium%20economy%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Wilson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20we%20do%20have%20a%20low-cost%20business%2C%20Air%20India%20Express.%20And%20so%2C%20for%20people%20that%20don't%20quite%20want%20those%20bells%20and%20whistles%20or%20prefer%20price%20over%20product%20and%20service%2C%20we%20will%20offer%20them%20a%20proposition%20as%20well.%20So%20really%20our%20portfolio%20approach%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20consumer.%20We%20don't%20necessarily%20dictate%20to%20the%20consumer%20what%20they%20should%20take%20from%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'Maharani'%20Soon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20airline%20changing%20its%20brand%20identity%20and%20livery%2C%20NDTV%20asked%20Mr%20Wilson%20whether%20Air%20India%20-%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20iconic%20Maharaja%20-%20could%20have%20a%20Maharani%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything's%20possible.%20I%20think%20let's%20just%20take%20it%20a%20step%20at%20a%20time.%20We've%20just%20released%20a%20new%20brand%2C%20people%20are%20still%20getting%20used%20to%20that%20new%20brand.%20We've%20said%20quite%20categorically%20that%20the%20Maharaja%20is%20part%20of%20the%20future%20Air%20India.%20It%20will%20have%20a%20certain%20manifestation%20closer%20to%20home%2C%20maybe%20a%20slightly%20different%20manifestation%20outside%20India.%20We'll%20see%20how%20it%20evolves.%20Air%20India%20will%20see%20new%20uniforms%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpgrading%20The%20Old%2C%20In%20With%20The%20New%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MD%20said%20Air%20India%20is%20refurbishing%20several%20aircraft%20as%20part%20of%20its%20long-term%20transformation%20plan%2C%20called%20'vihaan.AI'%20and%20that%20the%20airline%20wants%20to%20represent%20the%20new%20India%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bconfident%2C%20warm%20and%20hospitable%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20the%20airline%20wants%20the%20470%20new%20aircraft%2C%20which%20are%20coming%20in%2C%20to%20sit%20and%20grow%20on%20a%20strong%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20we%20committed%20to%20the%20%24400%20million%20for%20complete%20refurbishment%20of%20all%20of%20the%20wide-body%20aircraft%20with%20new%20seats%2C%20new%20in-flight%20entertainment%2C%20new%20galleys%2C%20new%20lavatories%20-%20essentially%20a%20complete%20replacement%20of%20the%20interior.%20Installation%20of%20the%20seats%20will%20commence%20on%20the%20first%20aircraft%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20next%20year%20in%20addition%20to%20those%20refurbished%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20aircraft%20that%20have%20been%20grounded%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20the%20effort%20-%20and%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20parts%20-%20that%20was%20needed%20to%20restore%20them%2C%20the%20MD%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20significant%20process%20because%20there%20were%2C%20if%20I%20recall%2C%20about%2030%20aircraft%20that%20had%20been%20grounded.%20I%20believe%20we've%20got%20two%20aircraft%2C%20two%20widebody%20aircraft%20at%20least%2C%20that%20are%20still%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20recovered.%20Some%20of%20these%20aircraft%20require%20thousands%20of%20parts.%20In%20totality%2C%20I%20think%20we're%20now%20up%20to%20about%2040%2C000%20parts%20that%20we've%20needed%20to%20acquire%20to%20get%20these%20aircraft%20airworthy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20world%20is%20undergoing%20a%20supply%20chain%20crunch%20and%20getting%20the%20parts%20and%20installing%20them%20has%20taken%20time.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we're%20nearly%20at%20the%20end%20of%20that%20journey%2C%20thankfully.%20That's%20what%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20increase%20service%20to%20five%20new%20cities%20already%20this%20year%2C%20international%20cities%2C%20and%20expand%20frequency%20on%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20of%20course%2C%20there's%20new%20aircraft%20we%20have%20coming%20in%20Thus%20far%2C%20we've%20got%20six%20777s%20that%20have%20%C2%A0already%20entered%20the%20fleet%20and%20are%20serving%20routes%20to%20North%20America%20and%20London.%20We%20have%20five%20more%20coming%20in%20over%20the%20next%20four-five%20months%20And%20we%20have%20six%20of%20our%20new%20A350s%20coming%20in%20before%20March%202024.%20Which%20will%20mean%20that.%20by%20March%202024%2C%20about%2030%25%20of%20our%20wide-body%20aircraft%20will%20be%20of%20a%20modern%20standard%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Wilson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Progress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20MD%20also%20praised%20the%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20progress%26quot%3B%20India%20has%20made%20in%20infrastructure%20development%20for%20civil%20aviation%2C%20and%20sounded%20very%20upbeat%20about%20the%20directions%20the%20airline%20could%20go%20in%2C%20and%20the%20new%20routes%20it%20could%20explore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20great%20thing%20about%20Indian%20aviation%20is%20that%20there%20are%20so%20many%20more%20opportunities%20than%20we%20have%20aircraft%20at%20the%20moment.%20So%20you%20could%20almost%20take%20your%20pick.%20There%20are%20many%20cities%20in%20North%20America%20that%20would%20warrant%20non-stop%20service%20from%20India%20-%20and%20not%20just%20from%20Delhi%2C%20from%20other%20markets.%20Likewise%2C%20Europe%2C%20Australia%2C%20Asia%2C%20Africa%20-%20I%20think%20there%20is%20a%20range%20of%20options%20and%20opportunities%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695745140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%