nt%20was%20found%20on%20Sangatte%20beach%20near%20Calais%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbody-of-migrant-found-on-sangatte-beach-near-calais-12970406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbody-of-migrant-found-on-sangatte-beach-near-calais-12970406%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbody-of-migrant-found-on-sangatte-beach-near-calais-12970406%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ashneer%20Grover%20Slams%20Rs%2055%2C000%20Crore%20Tax%20Notice%20To%20Gaming%20Firms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAshneer%20Grover%2C%20fantasy%20gaming%20app%20Crickpe's%20founder%2C%20in%20a%20strongly-worded%20tweet%2C%20slammed%20the%20tax%20authorities%20for%20issuing%20massive%20tax%20demand%20notices%20to%20gaming%20companies.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20GST%20Intelligence%20(DGGI)%20has%20issued%20pre-show%20cause%20notices%20to%2012%20online%20gaming%20companies%20worth%20Rs%2055%2C000%20crore.%20Dream11%2C%20the%20gaming%20unicorn%2C%20has%20received%20the%20largest%20tax%20notice%20for%20dues%20worth%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20BharatPe%20founder%20questioned%20the%20thought%20process%20of%20people%20running%20the%20tax%20department%20and%20said%20that%20their%20goal%20is%20just%20to%20''harass%20businessmen.''%20Ridiculing%20the%20exercise%2C%20he%20said%20that%20neither%20the%20people%20would%20pay%20the%20hefty%20taxes%2C%20nor%20would%20the%20government%20be%20able%20to%20collect%20them.%20The%20''game%20of%20monopoly''%20will%20only%20benefit%C2%A0lawyers%20who%20will%20challenge%20the%20policy%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr.%20Grover%20further%20remarked%20that%20this%20is%20called%20a%20'retrospective%20tax'.%20While%20Congress%20levied%20the%20Vodafone%20Retrospective%20Tax%2C%20BJP%20has%20come%20up%20with%20the%20Gaming%20GST%20Retrospective%20Tax%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20took%20a%20jibe%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20not%20helping%20the%20government's%20vision%20of%20achieving%20a%205%20trillion%20dollar%20economy%20and%20requested%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%20to%20address%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22et%5C%22%3E%E2%82%B955%2C000%20crore%20GST%20demand%20!%20I%20am%20intrigued%20ki%20Tax%20vaalo%20ke%20dimaag%20mein%20kya%20chalta%20hoga%20aise%20notice%20bhejte%20samay.%20The%20only%20explanation%20is%20-%20kuchh%20nahi.%20Monopoly%20ki%20game%20chal%20rahi%20hai%20bas.%20Na%20koi%20tax%20dega%20itna%20-%20na%20Sarkar%20ko%20milega.%20Milegi%20sirf%20vakilo%20ko%20fees%20jo%20SC%20mein%20ise%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FBB1b9g3R4E%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FBB1b9g3R4E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Ashneer%20Grover%20(%40Ashneer_Grover)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshneer_Grover%2Fstatus%2F1706577678235496466%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20tweet%2C%20one%20user%20said%2C%20''Despite%20all%20the%20talks%20about%20Ease%20of%20Doing%20Business%2C%20India%20needs%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20to%20truly%20become%20a%20business-friendly%20country.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''5%20tn%20economy%20was%20for%20the%20political%20class.%20Not%20for%20us%2C%20the%20people.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Grover%20has%20earlier%20slammed%20the%20move%20by%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20Council%20to%20impose%20a%2028%20percent%20tax%20on%20the%20turnover%20of%20online%20gaming%20companies.%20The%20online%20gaming%20industry%20has%20also%20said%20that%20levying%2028%20percent%20GST%20will%20limit%20their%20ability%20to%20invest%20in%20new%20games%20and%20impact%20cash%20flows%20as%20well%20as%20business%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0Mr%20Grover%20launched%20his%20own%20fantasy%20gaming%20named%20Crickpe%20in%20April%20this%20year%2C%20which%20allowed%20users%20to%20create%20a%20virtual%20team%20of%20cricketers%20based%20on%20their%20current%20form.%20Players%20earn%20points%20based%20on%20the%20cricketer's%20performance%20in%20a%20real%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695737520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F84pf3ooo_ashneer-grover_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fashneer-grover-slams-rs-55-000-crore-tax-notice-to-gaming-firms-harassing-businessmen-4425976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20BharatPe%20founder%20questioned%20the%20thought%20process%20of%20people%20running%20the%20tax%20department%20and%20said%20that%20their%20goal%20is%20just%20to%20''harass%20businessmen.''%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fashneer-grover-slams-rs-55-000-crore-tax-notice-to-gaming-firms-harassing-businessmen-4425976%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fashneer-grover-slams-rs-55-000-crore-tax-notice-to-gaming-firms-harassing-businessmen-4425976%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fashneer-grover-slams-rs-55-000-crore-tax-notice-to-gaming-firms-harassing-businessmen-4425976%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98American%20Delegation%20Visited%20Srinagar%20as%20Well%E2%80%99%3A%20US%20Envoy%20Eric%20Garcetti%20on%20Counterpart%E2%80%99s%20PoK%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F03090614%2FMorning_view_of_indus_river_in_skardu.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Af