2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ch%20Nageshu%20Patro%2C%20hailing%20from%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Ganjam%20district%2C%20left%20school%20because%20of%20poverty.%20Determined%20to%20prevent%20other%20children%20from%20facing%20the%20same%20situation%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20coolie%20at%20night%20and%20established%20a%20free%20coaching%20centre%20for%20underprivileged%20kids.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330903%2Fodisha-coolie-porter-nageshu-patro-teacher-runs-free-coaching-centre%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taapsee's%20next%20to%20release%20on%20October%2013%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695735009000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103965704%2Cimgsize-35926.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftaapsee-pannus-first-theatrical-film-as-a-producer-called-dhak-dhak-to-release-on-october-13%2Farticleshow%2F103965715.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103965715.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETaapsee%20Pannu%20is%20al%20set%20to%20release%20her%20first%20theatrical%20film%20as%20a%20producer%2C%20her%20film%20Dhak%20Dhak%20to%20release%20on%20October%2013th.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftaapsee-pannus-first-theatrical-film-as-a-producer-called-dhak-dhak-to-release-on-october-13%2Farticleshow%2F103965715.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'We%20won't%20back%20down'%3A%20Philippines%20warns%20China%20as%20row%20over%20disputed%20waters%20heats%20up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695734760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-philippine-south-china-sea_6298472.jpg%3F20230926103117%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fphilippines-cuts-chinese-barrier-and-issues-warning-as-row-over-disputed-waters-heats-up-12970372%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tensions%20are%20growing%20between%20the%20Philippines%20and%20China%20as%20a%20dispute%20over%20a%20fiercely-contested%20fishing%20area%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20escalated%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fphilippines-cuts-chinese-barrier-and-issues-warning-as-row-over-disputed-waters-heats-up-12970372%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fphilippines-cuts-chinese-barrier-and-issues-warning-as-row-over-disputed-waters-heats-up-12970372%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fphilippines-cuts-chinese-barrier-and-issues-warning-as-row-over-disputed-waters-heats-up-12970372%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20NREGA%20Job%20Card%20Deletions%20to%20Complex%20Aadhaar%20Mechanism%2C%20Tech%20Solutions%20Are%20Not%20the%20Answer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F21130014%2Fmgnrega-story.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20in%20India%2C%20which%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20work%20to%20rural%20households%2C%20has%20seen%20a%20significant%20issue%20of%20worker%20deletions%20from%20its%20database.%20In%20the%20fiscal%20year%202022-23%2C%20over%205.2%20crore%20workers%20were%20deleted%20from%20the%20system%2C%20representing%20a%20247%25%20increase%20in%20deletions%20compared%20to%20previous%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2023%2F38%2Fcommentary%2Faadhaar-mandate-mass-job-card-deletions.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20and%20Political%20Weekly%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20citing%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20(MoRD)%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20deletion%20and%20issuance%20of%20new%20job%20cards%20are%20routine%20practices%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20recent%20deletions%20has%20caused%20alarm.%20Job%20cards%20of%20deceased%20or%20migrated%20workers%20get%20deleted%20and%20new%20workers%20seeking%20employment%20have%20to%20get%20their%20names%20added%20or%20get%20a%20new%20job%20card%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20primary%20reason%20behind%20these%20deletions%20is%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Aadhaar-based%20Payment%20System%20(ABPS)%2C%20which%20has%20added%20complexity%20to%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20MoRD%20mandated%20the%20use%20of%20ABPS%20for%20processing%20all%20wage%20payments%20in%20MGNREGA%2C%20starting%20from%20February%201%2C%202023.%20However%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20mandate%2C%20only%2043%25%20of%20MGNREGA%20workers%20were%20eligible%20for%20ABPS%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20from%20MoRD%20to%20achieve%20100%25%20Aadhaar%20seeding%20(the%20process%20of%20workers%20submitting%20their%20Aadhaar%20details%20to%20be%20linked%20to%20their%20job%20cards)%20and%20authentication%20in%20a%20short%20period%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20worker%20deletions%20from%20the%20MGNREGA%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocal%20officials%2C%20lacking%20training%20and%20understanding%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20process%2C%20resorted%20to%20deleting%20ABPS-ineligible%20workers%20from%20the%20roster%20as%20an%20easier%20way%20to%20meet%20targets%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Faadhaar-payments-compulsory-nrega%5C%22%3EMaking%20Aadhaar-Based%20Payments%20Compulsory%20for%20Nrega%20Wages%20Is%20a%20Recipe%20for%20Disaster%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEPW%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexplains%20why%20deleting%20workers%20%E2%80%93%20without%20following%20due%20process%20%E2%80%93%20was%20easier%20for%20local%20officials.%20It%20explains%20three%20technical%20processes%20which%20need%20to%20be%20understood.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E1)%20Previously%2C%20workers%20had%20the%20option%20of%20linking%20their%20Aadhaar%20details%20to%20their%20job%20cards%20but%20it%20was%20not%20mandatory.%20Now%2C%20workers%20need%20an%20Aadhaar%20card%20to%20avail%20of%20MGNREGA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20August%2015%2C%20more%20than%206%20crore%20workers%20across%20the%20country%20did%20not%20complete%20Aadhaar%20seeding.%20These%20workers%20can%20no%20longer%20work%20under%20the%20MGNREGA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2)%20Aadhaar%20authentication%20involves%20the%20automatic%20verification%20of%20workers%E2%80%99%20details%20as%20registered%20in%20their%20job%20cards%20against%20their%20details%20in%20the%20Aadhaar%20database%2C%20including%20name%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20demographic%20details.%20If%20any%20discrepancies%20are%20found%2C%20the%20authentication%20fails.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20officials%20face%20challenges%20because%20they%20have%20not%20received%20guidelines%20for%20the%20resolution%20of%20mismatched%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20this%20issue%2C%20LibTech%20India%20filed%20an%20application%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%20with%20MoRD%20to%20inquire%20about%20the%20provisions%20or%20guidelines%20for%20worker%20deletions.%20They%20were%20provided%20with%20only%20a%20partial%20excerpt%20from%20the%20MGNREGA%20Annual%20Master%20Circular.%20It%20contained%20broad%20principles%20for%20deletions%20but%20lacked%20the%20detailed%20guidelines%20LibTech%20India%20had%20sought.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20across%20states%2C%20block%20data%20entry%20operators%20were%20rarely%20able%20to%20even%20locate%20lists%20of%20workers%20without%20Aadhaar%20seeding%20or%20authentication%2C%20let%20alone%20have%20knowledge%20of%20resolution%20procedures%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20enforcement.%20This%20confusion%20is%20not%20restricted%20to%20block%20officers%3B%20we%20have%20encountered%20significant%20misinformation%20about%20Aadhaar%20processes%20even%20with%20state-level%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3)%20Previously%2C%20MGNREGA%20wage%20payments%20could%20transferred%20via%20NEFT%2C%20but%20now%20ABPS%20is%20mandatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAadhaar-based%20payments%20use%20only%20the%20Aadhaar%20number%20as%20the%20financial%20address%20for%20where%20the%20payment%20goes.%20For%20ABPS%2C%20three%20linkages%20must%20be%20complete%3A%20first%2C%20a%20worker%E2%80%99s%20Aadhaar%20number%20must%20be%20seeded%20to%20her%20job%20card.%20Second%2C%20her%20Aadhaar%20must%20be%20seeded%20to%20her%20bank%20account%20via%20eKYC.%20Third%2C%20the%20worker%E2%80%99s%20Aadhaar%20must%20be%20linked%20to%20her%20bank%E2%80%99s%20Institutional%20Identification%20Number%20(IIN)%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98mapper%E2%80%9D%20(or%20database)%20created%20by%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%2C%20which%20acts%20as%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20payments%20clearing%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnly%20if%20all%20of%20these%20links%20are%20completed%2C%20will%20a%20worker%E2%80%99s%20wage%20payment%20be%20processed.%20With%20mandatory%20ABPS%2C%20even%20if%20a%20worker%20has%20worked%20under%20the%20MGNREGA%2C%20and%20if%20she%20is%20not%20eligible%20for%20ABPS%2C%20she%20cannot%20receive%20her%20wages%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EEPW%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20interventions%20appear%20to%20be%20complicated%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20approach%20should%20focus%20on%20strengthening%20infrastructure%2C%20better%20network%20coverage%2C%20and%20providing%20proper%20information%20and%20training%20for%20technical%20processes%20rather%20than%20hastily%20adopting%20complex%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Faadhaar-mgnrega-errors-corruption%5C%22%3EAadhaar%20in%20MGNREGA%20Is%20Likely%20to%20Be%20Hugely%20Disruptive%20for%20Workers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20%E2%80%9Cultimatum%20method%E2%80%9D%20to%20mandate%20Aadhaar%20seeding%2Fauthentication%20and%20ABPS%20in%20the%20MGNREGA%20programme%20has%20led%20to%20a%20dramatic%20247%25%20increase%20in%20job%20card%20deletions%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202022-23%20%E2%80%93%20with%20a%20drastic%202%2C700%25%20reported%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%E2%80%99s%20unclear%20how%20many%20of%20these%20deletions%20involve%20genuine%20or%20%E2%80%9Cfake%E2%80%9D%20workers%2C%20extensive%20fieldwork%20reveals%20that%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20vulnerable%2C%20real%20workers%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20their%20right%20to%20work%20and%20livelihood.%20Both%20authentication%20and%20ABPS%20create%20complex%20issues%20that%20are%20difficult%20to%20resolve%2C%20and%20the%20actual%20costs%20of%20addressing%20these%20issues%20often%20go%20unnoticed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20MGNREGA%20workers%20end%20up%20forgoing%20multiple%20days%20of%20work%20and%20spending%20money%20on%20food%20and%20travel%20as%20they%20navigate%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20which%20can%20be%20financially%20burdensome.%20These%20real-world%20costs%20should%20be%20considered%20when%20evaluating%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20such%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdigital-india-actually-made-mgnrega-less-transparent%5C%22%3Eseveral%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fblog%2Feconomy%2Fmgnrega-is-failing-10-reasons-why-62035%5C%22%3Equestions%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20raised%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20and%20problematic%20execution%20of%20the%20Aadhaar-implemented%20mechanisms%20in%20MGNREGA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20National%20Mobile%20Monitoring%20System%20(NMMS)%20app%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20without%20consulting%20MGNREGA%20workers%2C%20has%20faced%20numerous%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20app%20was%20launched%20after%20a%20pilot%20in%20one%20single%20district%2C%20and%20with%20zero%20worker%20consultation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20NMMS%20and%20Aadhaar%20seeding%2Fauthentication%20were%20intended%20to%20combat%20corruption%20in%20MGNREGA%2C%20but%20their%20implementation%20lacks%20evidence%20of%20success%20and%20has%20made%20workers%20suffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20implementing%20digital%20measures%20to%20address%20problems%20may%20be%20tempting%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20not%20reduce%20policymaking%20to%20techno-solutionism.%20Policy%20design%20for%20technical%20interventions%20must%20be%20consultative%2C%20properly%20piloted%2C%20and%20designed%20keeping%20the%20workers%20in%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695734155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F21130014%2Fmgnrega-story.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnrega-job-card-deletions-aadhaar-mechanism-tech-solutions-ineffective%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20FY23%2C%20over%205.2%20crore%20workers%20were%20deleted%20from%20the%20MGNREGA%20system%20%E2%80%93%20a%20247%25%20increase%20in%20deletions%20compared%20to%20previous%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnrega-job-card-deletions-aadhaar-mechanism-tech-solutions-ineffective%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zerodha%20profi