E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20also%20not%20the%20first%20instance%20when%20a%20Muslim%20leader%20was%20subjected%20to%20such%20derogatory%20treatment.%20Muslim%20politicians%20like%20Azam%20Khan%2C%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20Salman%20Khurshid%2C%20Badruddin%20Ajmal%2C%20the%20Abdullahs%2C%20the%20Muftis%2C%20and%20even%20former%20vice%20president%20Hamid%20Ansari%20have%20faced%20relentless%20demonisation%20by%20the%20TV%20news%20channels%20and%20social%20media%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-of-murder-attempt-on-akbaruddin-owaisi-court-acquits-prime-accused-convicts-4%2Fstory-WCRJnpvXyNhNuQdax8cdFP.html%5C%22%3Ethere%20was%20an%20attempt%20on%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%E2%80%99s%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsalman-khurshids-nainital-home-vandalised-days-after-controversy-over-hindutva-remarks-in-book%5C%22%3EKhurshid%E2%80%99s%20house%20was%20set%20ablaze%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20extends%20to%20all%20Muslim%20professionals.%20Whether%20you%E2%80%99re%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20or%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%2C%20whether%20you%20speak%20or%20go%20silent%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20guarantee%20that%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20hounded.%20As%20journalists%2C%20we%20often%20talk%20about%20the%20growing%20attack%20on%20free%20speech%20and%20the%20press%20but%20even%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20Muslim%20journalists%20stands%20out.%20The%20social%20media%20timelines%20of%20Rana%20Ayyub%2C%20Arfa%20Khanum%20and%20Mohammad%20Zubair%20show%20the%20variety%20of%20invectives%20that%20ordinary%20Muslims%20face%20in%20their%20daily%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20do%20you%20do%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20held%20responsible%20for%20the%20very%20crimes%20perpetrated%20against%20you%3B%20when%20somehow%20the%20reality%20of%20any%20crisis%20is%20always%20inverted%20and%20the%20truth%20is%20turned%20on%20its%20head%3F%20How%20would%20you%20respond%20to%20the%20bogus%20charges%20of%20%E2%80%98tomato%20jihad%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98juice%20jihad%E2%80%99%3F%20What%20do%20you%20do%20when%20all%20your%20words%20of%20endearment%20like%20%3Cem%3Eabbu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eammi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebhaijaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebaaji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebegum%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20robbed%20of%20their%20meanings%20and%20transformed%20into%20perverted%20pornographic%20connotations%3F%20What%20do%20you%20do%20when%20your%20mosques%2C%20style%20of%20worship%2C%20shrines%2C%20attire%2C%20heritage%2C%20festivals%2C%20appearance%2C%20language%2C%20citizenship%2C%20and%20food%20become%20a%20subject%20of%20persistent%20ridicule%3F%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20a%20fundamentally%20provocative%20armed%20mob%20that%20wants%20the%20right%20to%20march%20through%20your%20neighbourhood%20like%20an%20invading%20army%20while%20playing%20songs%20denigrating%20your%20existence%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F24104103%2FIMG_0291.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F24104103%2FIMG_0291.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F24104103%2FIMG_0291-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F24104103%2FIMG_0291-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-593503%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20have%20become%20like%20that%20bullied%20kid%20at%20school%20who%20is%20taunted%2C%20mocked%2C%20and%20assaulted%20by%20his%20classmates%2C%20and%20in%20the%20end%2C%20is%20punished%20by%20the%20teachers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20always%20the%20Muslim%20victim%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20BSP%20MP%2C%20who%20is%20held%20responsible%20for%20the%20provocation.%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20already%20started%20a%20dirty%20blame%20game%20against%20Ali.%20Propaganda%20handles%20claim%20that%20Ali%20refused%20to%20raise%20the%20slogan%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Glory%20to%20Mother%20India)%20on%20a%20certain%20occasion.%20Some%20went%20even%20one%20step%20ahead%20and%20called%20it%20a%20reaction%20to%20a%20Tamil%20politician%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%5C%22%3Eremarks%20against%20Sanatana%20Dharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20neither%20Ali%20nor%20any%20Muslim%20had%20a%20role%20to%20play.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20how%20the%20BJP%20machinery%20obfuscates%20facts%2C%20and%20rationalises%20its%20unjustifiable%20treatment%20of%20Muslims.%20Recall%20how%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20reacted%20to%20former%20US%20President%20Barack%20Obama%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20Indian%20minorities.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhussain-obama-himanta-biswa-sarma%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20%3C%2Fspan%3EHussain%3Cspan%3E%20Obama%20in%20India%20itself.%20We%20should%20prioritise%20taking%20care%20of%20them%20before%20considering%20going%20to%20Washington.%20The%20Assam%20police%20will%20act%20according%20to%20our%20own%20priorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuslims%20are%20not%20the%20only%20community%20facing%20persecution.%20There%20are%20cases%20of%20hate%20crimes%20against%20a%20Dalit%20or%20an%20Adivasi%20person%2C%20a%20Christian%20pastor%20is%20attacked%20or%20a%20church%20is%20vandalised.%20Sikhs%20are%20increasingly%20complaining%20about%20being%20targeted%20by%20right-wing%20forces%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20bogey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20pride%20with%20which%20Muslims%20are%20violated%20is%20absolutely%20unparalleled%20today.%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20recent%20outreach%20to%20Dalits%2C%20in%20which%20he%20talked%20about%20atonement%20even%20if%20it%20involves%20eating%20cow%20meat%2C%20still%20leaves%20space%20for%20cow%20vigilantes%20like%20Monu%20Manesar%20to%20do%20what%20they%20do%20%E2%80%93%20but%20only%20against%20Muslims.%20Contrast%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmp-man-urinate-tribal-youth-viral-video%5C%22%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chauhan%20washing%20the%20feet%20of%20a%20tribal%20man%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20urinated%20on%20by%20a%20BJP%20worker%2C%20with%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findore-bangle-seller-jail-assault%5C%22%3E%20unjust%20imprisonment%20of%20Tasleem%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bangle%20seller%20who%20was%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob%20and%20later%20incarcerated.%20The%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20with%20Muslims%2C%20the%20historical%20aggressor%20in%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20vision%2C%20the%20basic%20concepts%20of%20human%20decency%20vanish%2C%20the%20lines%20between%20lawful%20and%20unlawful%20are%20erased%2C%20and%20immorality%20becomes%20moral.%20This%20is%20why%20Zubair%20can%20be%20jailed%20for%20calling%20Bajrang%20Muni%2C%20the%20man%20who%20publicly%20called%20for%20the%20rape%20of%20Muslim%20women%2C%20a%20hate-monger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFatima%20Khan%2C%20a%20young%20Muslim%20journalist%20in%20Delhi%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20keep%20saying%20%E2%80%98nothing%20even%20shocks%20us%20anymore%E2%80%99%20and%20yet%20there%E2%80%99s%20something%20this%20country%20and%20its%20leaders%20do%20every%20now%20and%20then%20that%20comes%20as%20a%20gut%20punch.%E2%80%9D%20While%20some%20of%20us%20used%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cshocking%E2%80%9D%20and%20others%20used%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cunsurprising%E2%80%9D%20to%20try%20and%20aptly%20describe%20this%20explicit%20expression%20of%20disgust%20for%20Muslims%2C%20I%20think%20that%20in%20reality%2C%20Indian%20Muslims%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20accurate%20vocabulary%20to%20describe%20this%20everyday%20humiliation.%20Perhaps%2C%20we%20oscillate%20between%20a%20sense%20of%20astonishment%20and%20expectation%20because%20our%20reality%20is%20quite%20unpleasant%20%E2%80%93%20and%20just%20as%20any%20other%20group%20of%20humans%2C%20we%20can%20never%20make%20peace%20with%20being%20dehumanised.%20Our%20real%20quest%20is%20to%20find%20the%20language%20in%20which%20we%20can%20forcefully%20articulate%20and%20protest%20our%20dehumanisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695732049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-it-means-indian-muslim-today%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri's%20slurs%20against%20Danish%20Ali%20went%20viral%2C%20some%20of%20us%20Muslims%20expressed%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20astonishment%20and%20others%2C%20the%20total%20lack%20of%20it.%20Indian%20Muslims%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20accurate%20vocabulary%20to%20describe%20the%20everyday%20humiliations%20we%20face.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-it-means-indian-muslim-today%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bollywood%20actresses%20acing%20festive%20saree