%20Fox%20Corporation%20and%20News%20Corp%20but%20will%20stay%20on%20in%20the%20role%20of%20chairman%20emeritus%2C%20presumably%20to%20help%20guide%20his%20eldest%20son%20Lachlan%20as%20the%20new%20head%20of%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20the%20news%20was%20inevitable.%20The%20company%20is%20clearly%20planning%20its%20succession%20and%20how%20it%20manages%20Rupert%E2%80%99s%20decline.%20It%20has%20one%20eye%20on%20the%20market%20and%20one%20on%20ensuring%20the%20company%20maintains%20its%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20now%2C%20and%20where%20to%20from%20here%20for%20the%20company%3F%20And%20what%20will%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20be%20remembered%20for%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERupert%E2%80%99s%20departure%20was%20always%20going%20to%20come%20in%20one%20of%20two%20ways%3A%20either%20Rupert%20dropping%20off%20the%20perch%20or%20him%20leaving%20on%20this%20own%20terms.%20He%20has%20opted%20for%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20the%20company%20has%20chosen%20to%20manage%20the%20transition%20in%20a%20market-favourable%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20to%20Lachlan%20looks%2C%20for%20the%20moment%2C%20to%20be%20well%20and%20truly%20secure.%20This%20gives%20him%20the%20chance%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Rupert%20to%20guide%20the%20company%20in%20the%20direction%20he%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Rupert%20%E2%80%93%20wants.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERupert%20says%20he%20is%20in%20robust%20health%20but%20he%20was%20keen%20to%20hang%20on%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%20So%2C%20perhaps%20today%E2%80%99s%20news%20suggests%20his%20health%20is%20declining.%20We%20can%20only%20speculate%20but%20the%20man%20is%2C%20after%20all%2C%2092.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20the%20recent%20lawsuits%20have%20played%20a%20role%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFox%20has%20been%20subject%20to%20several%20very%20expensive%20lawsuits%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20which%20caused%20a%20lot%20of%20turmoil%20internally.%20At%20the%20cost%20of%20US%24787.5%20million%2C%20Fox%20settled%20a%20defamation%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20Dominion%20Voting%20Systems%20over%20baseless%20claims%20made%20about%20its%20voting%20machines%20in%20the%202020%20US%20presidential%20election.%20A%20different%20voting%20technology%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fmedia%2F2023%2Fsep%2F21%2Frupert-murdoch-fox-news-lawsuits-donald-trump%5C%22%3ESmartmatic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20also%20suing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20doubt%20this%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20Rupert%20stepping%20down%20because%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20a%20billion%20in%20lawsuits%20is%20nothing%20to%20a%20company%20that%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20made%20%2470%20billion%20by%20selling%20just%20some%20of%20its%20assets%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fbrianbushard%2F2023%2F09%2F21%2Ffox-and-news-corp-stock-surges-as-rupert-murdoch-steps-down%2F%3Fsh%3D37463b772a49%5C%22%3EDisney%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20price%20the%20company%20pays%20for%20its%20take-no-prisoners%20approach.%20It%20is%20proud%20of%20its%20uncompromising%20editorial%20stance%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20pander%20to%20its%20right-wing%20audience.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20indication%20Lachlan%20will%20take%20it%20in%20a%20different%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20next%20for%20Lachlan%2C%20with%20Rupert%20as%20chairman%20emeritus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sense%2C%20Rupert%20is%20not%20really%20stepping%20down.%20His%20new%20papal-like%20title%20of%20chairman%20emeritus%20recognises%20he%20will%20struggle%20to%20let%20go.%20But%20the%20new%20role%20is%20also%20about%20calming%20the%20market%20and%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20worry%2C%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20gone%20away%3B%20I%20am%20still%20here%20and%20I%20have%20my%20hand%20on%20Lachlan%E2%80%99s%20shoulder.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20indication%20of%20Lachlan%E2%80%99s%20future%20stewardship%20of%20News%20Corp%20is%20his%20recent%20behaviour.%20He%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20Fox%20News%20during%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20years%20and%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%2C%20when%20Fox%20News%20did%20enormous%20damage%20in%20its%20reporting%20on%20the%202020%20election%20result.%20He%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20when%20Fox%20was%20making%20those%20baseless%20claims%20about%20Dominion%20Voting%20Systems.%20He%20had%20ample%20opportunity%20to%20guide%20the%20company%20in%20a%20different%20direction%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20think%20we%20can%20expect%20News%20Corp%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20zealous%20right-wing%20media%20company%20it%20currently%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20might%20this%20affect%20the%202024%20US%20election%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENews%20Corp%20has%20finally%20seen%20what%20millions%20of%20US%20voters%20saw%20at%20the%202020%20election%2C%20which%20was%20that%20Trump%20was%20ultimately%20destructive%20as%20a%20leader.%20Now%2C%20outlets%20like%20Fox%20News%20are%20umming%20and%20ahhing%20about%20whether%20to%20back%20him.%20Some%20at%20Fox%20are%20clearly%20reluctant%20to%20let%20go%20of%20their%20adoration%20of%20Trump%20while%20others%20are%20disappointed%20Florida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20emerging%20as%20a%20viable%20challenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Trump%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20most%20popular%20Republican%20candidate%2C%20Fox%20will%20probably%20fall%20into%20line%20and%20support%20him%2C%20albeit%20with%20less%20enthusiasm%20than%20last%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20confusion%20within%20Fox%20about%20whom%20to%20back%20and%20where%20to%20stand%2C%20which%20reflects%20the%20chaos%20in%20US%20politics%20more%20broadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%