in-a-cameo-in-fukrey-3-hints-about-its-next-instalment-report%2Farticleshow%2F103961848.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20%E2%80%98Make%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20Enters%2010th%20Year%2C%20What%20Does%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Silence%20Mean%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26163721%2FNarendra_Modi_launches_Make_in_India.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20September%2025%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20programme%20Make%20in%20India%20entered%20its%20tenth%20year.%20For%20a%20government%20that%20thrives%20on%20events%20and%20celebrating%20fiction%2C%20there%20was%20an%20eerie%20silence%20during%20the%20lead-up%20to%20this%20important%20anniversary.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20government%20has%20accepted%20that%20glitzy%20PR%20is%20no%20longer%20sufficient%20to%20hide%20the%20perilously%20weakened%20manufacturing%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMake%20in%20India%20was%20launched%20with%20much%20fanfare%2C%20with%20the%20government%20listing%20for%20itself%20three%20major%20targets%3A%20a)%20increasing%20manufacturing%20growth%20by%2012-14%25%20per%20annum%20b)%20increasing%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20GDP%20to%2025%25%20by%202022%20c)%20creating%20100%20million%20jobs%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20by%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20the%20lack%20of%20celebrations%20is%20because%20not%20a%20single%20target%20has%20been%20achieved.%20The%20manufacturing%20growth%20rate%20has%20averaged%205.9%25%20since%202013-14%2C%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20has%20remained%20stagnant%20and%20was%20at%2016.4%25%20in%202022-23%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy-make-in-india-half-of-manufacturing-jobs-lost-in-five-years-2256758%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFrom%2520employing%252051%2520million%2520people%2Ccrisis%2520caused%2520by%2520the%2520pandemic.%5C%22%3Emanufacturing%20jobs%20halved%20between%202016%20and%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20decade%20of%20Make%20in%20India%20saw%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20workforce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Findias-manufacturing-sector-faces-worsening-decline-implications-for-growth-employment-and-income-11686851477882.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEven%2520by%2520share%2520of%2520employment%2C11.6%2525%2520in%25202021%252D22.%5C%22%3Edecline%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%2012.6%25%20in%202011-12%20to%2011.6%25%20in%202021-22.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20all-around%20poor%20performance%20has%20not%20deterred%20the%20government%20from%20passing%20off%20exceptional%20events%20as%20regular%20affairs.%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20iPhone%20manufacturing%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%20Reportedly%2C%20Apple%20has%20tripled%20iPhone%20production%20in%20India%20and%20almost%207%25%20of%20devices%20are%20now%20manufactured%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20government%20and%20its%20cheerleaders%20have%20chosen%20to%20propagate%20this%20data%20point%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20manufacturing%20clout.%20A%20quick%20look%20at%20the%20figures%20is%20enough%20to%20dispel%20such%20notions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Index%20of%20Industrial%20Production%20(IIP)%20tracks%20growth%20in%20different%20industry%20groups.%20India%E2%80%99s%20IIP%20has%20grown%20from%20106.7%20in%202013-14%20to%20138.5%20in%202022-23%2C%20at%20a%20yearly%20average%20of%202.9%25.%20A%20thriving%20manufacturing%20industry%20must%20showcase%20annual%20growth%20of%207-8%25.%20Since%202014%2C%20most%20sectors%20have%20been%20struggling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sobering%20reality%20is%20that%20growth%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20electrical%20equipment%20has%20averaged%20(-)1.8%25%20since%202013-14.%20The%20average%20growth%20of%20the%20computer%2C%20electronic%2C%20and%20optical%20products%20sector%20has%20been%202%25%2C%20the%20transport%20equipment%20industry%20has%20grown%20at%202.3%25%2C%20and%20motor%20vehicle%20production%20has%20grown%20at%201.6%25.%20Textile%2C%20apparel%2C%20and%20leather%20industries%20have%20traditionally%20been%20job-creating%20sectors.%20They%20have%20grown%20at%20rates%20of%20(-)0.5%25%2C%201.2%25%2C%20and%20(-)1.8%25%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20massive%20joblessness%20%E2%80%93%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20amongst%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2F42-3-of-graduates-under-25-unemployed-finds-latest-state-of-working-india-report-8949124%2F%5C%22%3Eyoung%20graduates%20is%2042.3%25%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20because%20manufacturing%20has%20failed%20to%20take%20off.%20Apple%20expanding%20its%20production%20base%20in%20India%20is%20motivating%20but%20not%20the%20complete%20picture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20factory%20here%20and%20a%20factory%20there%20is%20not%20the%20way%20to%20go.%20India%20needs%20hundreds%20of%20new%20factories%20across%20states%20that%20manufacture%20products%20consumed%20by%20different%20classes.%20The%20Annual%20Survey%20of%20Industries%20underscores%20how%20the%20sector%20has%20lost%20all%20vibrancy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20number%20of%20factories%20increased%20by%20almost%20a%20lakh%20during%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government.%20Between%202013-14%20and%202019-20%2C%20the%20number%20increased%20by%20only%2022%2C000.%20The%20manufacturing%20surge%20during%20the%20UPA%20led%20to%20more%20employment%20opportunities.%20The%20number%20of%20employees%20in%20factories%20grew%20at%206.2%25%20annually%20during%20the%20UPA%20regime.%20This%20growth%20fell%20to%202.8%25%20under%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Similarly%2C%20wages%20to%20workers%20grew%20at%2017.1%25%20annually%20under%20the%20UPA%2C%20falling%20to%208.4%25%20since%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfits%20of%20factories%20were%20increasing%20at%2018.9%25%20annually%20during%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20term%20and%20now%20stand%20at%200.6%25.%20Before%20marketing%20and%20sloganeering%20took%20over%20sound%20policymaking%2C%20a%20government%20worked%20diligently%20and%20the%20results%20speak%20for%20themselves.%20More%20factories%20were%20set%20up%2C%20more%20workers%20hired%2C%20workers%20paid%20reasonable%20amounts%2C%20and%20proprietors%20made%20handsome%20profits.%20This%20climate%20inspired%20industries%20to%20invest%20heavily%20in%20the%20sector.%20Gross%20capital%20formation%20under%20the%20UPA%20averaged%2021.3%25%20and%20has%20since%20turned%20negative%20(-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E0.7%25).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lack%20of%20investments%20is%20a%20telltale%20sign%20of%20loss%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies.%20A%20year%20ago%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Fwhy-is-indian-industry-hesitant-to-invest-in-manufacturing-nirmala-sitharaman-asks-india-inc-news-223141%5C%22%3Eadmonished%3C%2Fa%3E%20industry%20leaders%20for%20not%20investing%20in%20manufacturing.%20She%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20equally%20want%20to%20know%20from%20the%20Indian%20industry%20why%20they%20are%20hesitant%20(to%20invest)%20%E2%80%A6We%20will%20do%20everything%20to%20get%20the%20industry%20to%20invest%20here%20%E2%80%A6%20(but)%20I%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20India%20Inc%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20stopping%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20she%20received%20an%20answer%20that%20day%20but%20we%20do%20know%20that%20the%20economy%20still%20suffers%20from%20a%20demand%20slump.%20There%20are%20no%20investments%20in%20manufacturing%20because%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20demand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20manufacturing%20sector%20may%20have%20been%20on%20a%20different%20trajectory%20without%20policy%20missteps%20like%20demonetisation%20and%20the%20poorly%20designed%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax.%20The%20latter%20struck%20at%20the%20low%20margins%20of%20the%20MSMEs.%20The%20little%20recovery%20was%20wiped%20out%20with%20the%20announcement%20of%20an%20unplanned%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20in%20March%202020.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20response%20continues%20to%20be%20insipid.%20Raising%20import%20duties%20and%20prescribing%20licensing%20requirements%20does%20not%20enthuse%20businesses%20or%20foreign%20manufacturers%20looking%20to%20diversify%20operations%20as%20part%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98China%20Plus%20One%E2%80%99%20strategy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWeakened%20manufacturing%20has%20hurt%20India%20more%20than%20the%20data%20reflects.%20Although%20unwittingly%2C%20the%20most%20trenchant%20criticism%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20economic%20policies%20came%20from%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar.%20In%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fveterans-criticise-jaishankar-china%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Jaishankar%20candidly%20confessed%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20economic%20might%20comes%20in%20the%20way%20of%20how%20this%20government%20deals%20with%20the%20border%20transgression%20issue.%20The%20minister%E2%80%99s%20defeatist%20attitude%20does%20our%20position%20and%20security%20forces%E2%80%99%20morale%20no%20good.%20It%20does%20raise%20questions%20within%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20decade%20is%20a%20long%20time%20to%20judge%20a%20policy.%20If%20a%20programme%20repeatedly%20fails%2C%20it%20may%20be%20evidence%20that%20there%20is%20time%20to%20shelve%20it%20for%20something%20effective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAkash%20Satyawali%20is%20a%20public%20policy%20professional%20and%20National%20Coordinator%2C%20AICC%20Research%20Department.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695727049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26163721%2FNarendra_Modi_launches_Make_in_India.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmake-in-india-10-years-government-silence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20a%20government%20that%20thrives%20on%20events%20and%20celebration%2C%20the%20eerie%20silence%20during%20the%20lead-up%20to%20this%20important%20anniversary%20is%20a%20possible%20indication%20that%20it%20has%20accepted%20that%20glitzy%20PR%20is%20no%20longer%20sufficient%20to%20hide%20the%20perilously%20weakened%20manufacturing%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmake-in-india-10-years-government-silence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manhunt%20for%20gang%20boss%20who%20controlled%20luxury%20jail%20in%20Venezuela%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695726797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FC5E9%2Fproduction%2F_131256605_capture.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-66922730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22H%C3%A9ctor%20Guerrero%20Flores%20escaped%20shortly%20before%20the%20jail%20which%20he%20controlled%20was%20raided%20by%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A188%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-66922730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-66922730.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-66922730.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teenagers%20in