%20autism%20spectrum%2C%20first%20found%20out%20about%20this%20product%20through%20a%20friend.%20Upon%20hearing%20about%20it%2C%20he%20found%20that%20it%20was%20a%20well%20thought%20out%20and%20sensitive%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20son%20went%20missing%20for%20just%2010%20minutes%20in%20a%20zoo%2C%20it%20was%20a%20horrendous%20experience%20for%20us.%20I%20had%20also%20seen%20a%20child%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20local%20train%20who%20seemed%20to%20be%20lost.%20I%20immediately%20handed%20him%20over%20to%20the%20railway%20police%20at%20Vikhroli%20station.%20Such%20a%20QR%20tag%20is%20very%20beneficial%20for%20children%20on%20the%20spectrum%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkshay%20had%20previously%20created%20such%20QR%20tags%20for%20stray%20dogs%20as%20well%2C%20in%20February%202023.%20He%20was%20triggered%20to%20do%20this%20after%20his%20dog%20went%20missing.%20This%20particular%20QR%20code%20gives%20the%20name%2C%20gender%2C%20caretaker%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20phone%20number%20and%20vaccination%2Fsterilisation%20history%20of%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20both%20these%20innovations%20are%20much-needed%2C%20they%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20awareness%20to%20succeed%20on%20a%20grand%20scale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20authorities%2C%20especially%20the%20railway%20police%2C%20need%20to%20be%20told%20about%20these%20QR%20codes.%20A%20lot%20of%20awareness%20is%20needed%20to%20make%20people%20acquainted%20with%20this%20product.%20Above%20all%2C%20people%20need%20to%20have%20a%20little%20more%20empathy%2C%20and%20be%20more%20forthcoming.%20When%20you%20see%20someone%20in%20distress%2C%20you%20need%20to%20try%20and%20help%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rajagopal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETarun%20Gupta%2C%20who%20went%20missing%20in%20October%202019%2C%20has%20still%20not%20been%20found.%20Akshay%20hopes%20to%20prevent%20any%20other%20parent%20from%20going%20through%20such%20a%20harrowing%20ordeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20out%20more%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fprojectchetna.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F36637034%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENCBI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworldpopulationreview.com%2Fcountry-rankings%2Fmissing-persons-statistics-by-country%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWorld%20population%20review%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695385883000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshay%20Ridlan%20has%20come%20up%20with%20a%20QR-based%20digital%20identification%20system%20to%20locate%20people%20who%20lose%20their%20way.%20His%20innovation%2C%20a%20pendant%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20in%20it%2C%20would%20be%20beneficial%20for%20people%20with%20dementia%20and%20Alzheimer's%20and%20children%20with%20disabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330545%2Fakshay-ridlan-qr-code-locket-finding-lost-missing-people-dementia-autism-upsc%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Retd%20Army%20Major%26nbsp%3Bis%20on%20a%20Mission%20to%20Make%20Adventure%20Sports%20Inclusive%20for%20People%20With%20Disabilities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20various%20points%20in%20our%20lives%2C%20we%20all%20grapple%20with%20the%20time