2C%20and%20mountaineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20prompted%20this%20profound%20shift%20from%20seeking%20respite%20to%20founding%20an%20organisation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20military%20service%20to%20empowering%20the%20disabled%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20part%20of%209%20Para%20Special%20Forces%2C%20in%202015%2C%20Major%20Vivek%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20while%20training%20and%20injured%20his%20spine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20he%20met%20Flight%20Lieutenant%20Bhaduria%20who%20was%20paralysed%20waist%20down%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%20due%20to%20an%20accident.%20The%20lieutenant%20had%20dived%20into%20a%20pool%20and%20hit%20his%20head%2C%20injuring%20his%20neck%20which%20left%20him%20paralysed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20time%20in%20the%20military%20hospital%2C%20as%20I%20recovered%2C%20I%20closely%20observed%20how%20hard%20my%20friend%E2%80%99s%20life%20was.%20He%20was%20suffering%20and%20losing%20hope%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCTsIGnpIHeu%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCTsIGnpIHeu%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20