20impairment%2C%20hails%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20She%20was%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20people%20in%20the%20Siachen%20expedition.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20surreal%20experience.%20I%20never%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20make%20it.%20I%20was%20the%20only%20woman%20on%20the%20expedition.%20We%20had%20to%20walk%20for%20hours%20in%20a%20day%20but%20it%20was%20all%20worth%20it.%20Before%20going%20on%20the%20expedition%2C%20my%20teammates%20and%20I%20underwent%20a%20series%20of%20training%20sessions%20for%2015%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20easy%2C%20but%20the%20success%20of%20the%20expedition%20helped%20me%20gain%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence.%20Since%20there%20were%20other%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20whenever%20I%20felt%20like%20giving%20up%2C%20they%20supported%20me%20and%20gave%20me%20confidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Major%20also%20has%20plans%20to%20expand%20the%20Land%20World%20Record%20programme%20into%20Air%20and%20Water%20World%20Record%20programmes%20where%20he%20will%20train%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20to%20do%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309739%2Fmajor-devender-pal-singh-injured-in-kargil-asia-first-disabled-solo-skydiver%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20independent%20sky%20diving%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20water%20diving.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20work%20so%20far%2C%20Major%20Vivek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20people%20look%20at%20disabilities%20with%20sympathy%20but%20we%20look%20for%20the%20ability%20in%20the%20disability.%20Every%20person%20has%20an%20inner%20potential%20that%20they%20need%20to%20realise%2C%20once%20you%20do%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20stopping%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20person%20with%20a%20disability%20and%20want%20to%20experience%20adventure%20sports%20with%20Major%20Vivek%2C