p%3EAlong%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20Monalisa%20Mohanty%20(53)%2C%20his%20outfit%20has%20gained%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20about%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20a%20feat%20which%20they%20managed%20to%20achieve%20in%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F240644%2Findia-orchid-how-to-grow-business-flower-cultivation-import-industrialist-horticulture-department-telangana-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorchid%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20feat%2C%20Sujan%20shares%20what%20qualities%20are%20required%20to%20make%20this%20a%20fruitful%20vocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20should%20have%20patience%20and%20perseverance%20to%20take%20up%20this%20task.%20One%20has%20to%20wait%20for%20two%20years%20for%20a%20suitable%20and%20proper%20yield%20at%20first.%20An%20acre%20of%20land%20may%20only%20produce%2060%2C000%20flowers%2C%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20but%20wait%20and%20watch%20in%20wonder%20how%20that%20number%20slowly%20shoots%20up%20to%20almost%20two%20lakhs%20soon.%20My%20training%20in%20the%20army%20has%20helped%20me%20immensely%20with%20this%20profession.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20reason%20why%20I%20am%20now%20able%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20wife%20of%20an%20army%20man%2C%20I%20have%20been%20ingrained%20with%20these%20traits%20as%20well.%20I%20have%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20robust%20support%20system%20both%20in%20his%20personal%20and%20professional%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Monalisa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20Sujan%20before%20he%20decided%20on%20orchid%20cultivation%2C%20a%20venture%20which%20is%20totally%20alien%20to%20him.%20But%20with%20pure%20dedication%20and%20determination%2C%20his%20idea%20took%20root%20and%20then%20there%20was%20no%20turning%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mohantys%20with%20visitors%20at%20their%20farm.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130-1536x1023.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Mohantys%20with%20visitors%20at%20their%20farm.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20%E2%80%98Orchids%20N%20More%E2%80%99%20came%20to%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESujan%20had%20been%20in%20a%20fix%20over%20his%20future%20after%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F285608%2Fretired-kochi-scientist-how-to-grow-orchids-organic-vegetables-at-home-tips-hacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202012.%20He%20wanted%20to%20break%20into%20a%20new%20venture%20but%20was%20baffled%20by%20the%20number%20of%20options%20available.%20His%20interest%2C%20however%2C%20lay%20in%20floriculture.%20But%20he%20knew%20he%20needed%20time%20to%20make%20a%20wise%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20he%C2%A0proceeded%20to%20join%20Bengaluru-based%20Caf%C3%A9%20Coffee%20Day%20Group%20as%20the%20head%20of%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20there%20for%20one%20year%2C%20he%20switched%20over%20to%20Adani%20Group%20as%20the%20head%20of%20operations%20in%20Ahmedabad%20till%202016.%20Then%20he%20returned%20to%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20where%20he%20was%20born%20and%20brought%20up%2C%20to%20settle%20down.%20Here%20he%20joined%20a%20civil%20engineering%20consultancy%20firm%20called%20Op%20%26amp%3B%20Hs%20Infra%20as%20director-partner.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20army%20man%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20idle.%20The%20jobs%20not%20only%20kept%20me%20busy%20but%20also%20gave%20me%20time%20to%20research%20different%20types%20of%20floriculture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sujan%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20something%20was%20amiss.%20The%20nagging%20sense%20of%20doing%20something%20of%20his%20own%20kept%20him%20busy.%20He%20went%20on%20researching%2C%20surfing%20the%20internet%2C%20debating%20and%20discussing%20different%20business%20venture%20ideas%20with%20his%20friends%20and%20wife.%20Finally%2C%20in%202017%2C%20the%20Mohantys%20zeroed%20in%20on%20orchid%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20once%20toyed%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20rose%20cultivation.%20When%20I%20learnt%20that%20the%20longevity%20of%20a%20plucked%20rose%20is%20two%20to%20three%20days%20and%20that%20of%20an%20orchid%E2%80%99s%20vase%20(a%20set-up%20of%20coconut%20husks%20where%20orchids%20grow)%20is%2020%20to%2030%20days%2C%20I%20opted%20for%20this%20instead%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sujan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20came%20with%20its%20own%20set%20of%20problems.%20For%20one%2C%20he%20had%20no%20land%20or%20funds%20to%20support%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMonalisha-with-workers-in-orchid-poly-house_11zon-1695306227.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Monalisa%20Mohanty%20with%20the%20workers%20of%20their%20farm%20checking%20up%20on%20the%20flowers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMonalisha-with-workers-in-orchid-poly-house_11zon-1695306227.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMonalisha-with-workers-in-orchid-poly-house_11zon-1695306227-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMonalisha-with-workers-in-orchid-poly-house_11zon-1695306227-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMonalisha-with-workers-in-orchid-poly-house_11zon-1695306227-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMonalisha-with-workers-in-orchid-poly-house_11zon-1695306227-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMonalisha-with-workers-in-orchid-poly-house_11zon-1695306227-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FMonalisha-with-workers-in-orchid-poly-house_11zon-1695306227-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330579%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMonalisa%20Mohanty%20with%20the%20workers%20of%20their%20farm%20checking%20up%20on%20the%20flowers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20research%20and%20efforts%20that%20went%20into%20setting%20it%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESujan%20then%20met%20experts%20from%20Odisha%20University%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Technology%20(OUAT)%20and%20various%20orchid%20growers%20in%20Huma%20of%20Ganjam%20district%20to%20get%20the%20hang%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20and%20I%20toured%20across%20India%20for%20eight%20months%20in%202018%20to%20meet%20the%20farmers%20there%20and%20get%20hands-on%20knowledge%20of%20the%20skill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20places%20that%20they%20toured%20were%20Siliguri%20in%20Assam%2C%20Shillong%20in%20Meghalaya%2C%20and%20Baramati%20near%20Pune%20in%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKitted%20out%20with%20preliminary%20knowledge%2C%20the%20couple%20geared%20up%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20into%20farming.%20They%20procured%20a%20patch%20of%202%2C500%20sq%20ft%20on%20lease%20from%20an%20abandoned%20farm%20of%20nearly%2015%20acres%20in%20Kantapada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20secured%20a%20loan%20of%20about%20Rs%2024%20lakh%20with%20some%2050%20percent%20subsidy%20from%20the%20horticulture%20department%20in%20the%20Khordha%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Debasish%20Mishra%2C%20the%20assistant%20director%20(horticulture)%2C%20Khordha%2C%20explains%20how%20the%20scheme%20for%20people%20interested%20in%20the%20career%20works.%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20Protected%20Cultivation%20Component%20of%20Mission%20for%20Integrated%20Development%20of%20Horticulture%20(MIDH)%20of%20the%20central%20government%2C%20the%20scheme%20promotes%20different%20horticulture%20sectors%20that%20include%20flowers%2C%20aromatic%20plants%2C%20vegetables%2C%20tuber%20crops%20roots%20and%20mushrooms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAvailing%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20this%20scheme%2C%20Sujan%20set%20up%20a%20polyhouse%20%E2%80%94%20a%20type%20of%20specialised%20structure%20that%20utilises%20controlled%20climatic%20conditions%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20plants%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20land%20to%20house%20orchid%20saplings.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFlowers%20like%20orchids%20can%20grow%20well%20inside%20a%20polyhouse%20when%20the%20temperature%20is%2020%20to%2025%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%20humidity%20ranges%20between%2040%20to%2070%20percent.%20Besides%2C%20a%20micro-irrigation%20set-up%20is%20an%20added%20fixture%20as%20orchids%20require%20little%20water.%20However%2C%20quantifying%20the%20water%20requirement%20is%20difficult%20as%20it%20differs%20from%20species%20to%20species%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20(Prof)%20Sharat%20Chandra%20Sahoo%20of%20the%20department%20of%20fruit%20science%20and%20horticulture%20of%20OUAT.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Mohantys%20then%20proceeded%20to%20get%20white%20and%20purple%20orchid%20saplings%20from%20Bengaluru%20as%20the%20city%20has%20the%20best%20varieties%20of%20orchids%20available.%20They%20hired%20around%2025%20local%20labourers%20to%20get%20started%20with%20the%20farm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOther%20obstacles%20along%20their%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Chandaka%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20flanking%20the%20farm%2C%20there%20was%20a%20fear%20of%20wild%20animals%20such%20as%20elephants%2C%20boars%20and%20deer%20coming%20and%20ruining%20the%20plot.%20The%20presence%20of%20venomous%20snakes%20was%20another%20big%20issue%20that%20haunted%20Sujan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20set%20up%20a%20solar%20fence%20around%20the%20polyhouse%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20about%20Rs%206%20lakh.%20I%20kept%20pots%20with%20carbolic%20acid%20at%20their%20entry%20points%2C%20the%20smell%20of%20which%20supposedly%20keeps%20snakes%20away.%20I%20learnt%20this%20information%20from%20the%20internet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sujan%2C%20reporting%20that%20this%20trick%20has%20so%20far%20worked%20very%20well%20on%20the%20farm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20odds%20were%20still%20stacked%20against%20him%20as%20the%20orchids%20started%20blooming%20in%20the%20polyhouse%20only%20after%2010%20months.%20They%20were%20small%20in%20size%20and%20failed%20to%20click%20with%20the%20flower%20market%20of%20Cuttack%20and%20Bhubaneswar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20there%20is%20said%20to%20have%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%2C%20where%20orchids%20have%20a%20share%20of%20nearly%20eight%20percent.%C2%A0Sujan%2C%20however%2C%20bided%20his%20time.%20Once%20his%20orchids%20grew%20in%20shape%20and%20size%2C%20they%20started%20to%20sell%3Cs%3E%20%3C%2Fs%3Ebetween%20Rs%2015%20and%20Rs%2030.%20He%20also%20managed%20the%20sales%20and%20marketing%20functions%20of%20the%20farm%20and%20soon%20the%20business%20started%20picking%20up%20momentum.%20Their%20business%20even%20forayed%20into%20the%20markets%20of%20Kolkata%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Hyderabad%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENatural%20disasters%20played%20a%20dampener%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20Mohantys%20began%20reaping%20the%20results%20of%20their%20hard%20work%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320695%2Fodisha-ias-officer-pradeep-kumar-jena-leads-cyclone-disaster-response%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecyclone%20Fani%3C%2Fa%3E%20struck%20in%20May%202019.%20The%20roof%20of%20the%20polyhouse%20was%20blown%20away%20and%20a%20part%20of%20its%20boundary%20wall%20collapsed%20during%20the%20stormy%20downpour.%20The%20couple%20had%20to%20spend%20over%20Rs%206%20lakh%20from%20their%20personal%20savings%20to%20reset%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20disaster%20was%20soon%20followed%20by%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%20March%202020%2C%20bringing%20everything%20to%20a%20standstill.%20Monalisa%20%E2%80%94%20who%20looks%20after%20the%20management%20of%20the%20polyhouse%20and%20operations%20inside%20it%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20these%20setbacks%20leave%20them%20nonplussed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%