erindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-2-1695300985-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-2-1695300985-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330489%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESonali%20was%20also%20a%20probationary%20trainee%20at%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20in%20her%20early%20career%20days.%C2%A0Picture%20credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20the%20situation%20then%2C%20she%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20express%20enough%20gratitude%20for%20my%20parents%E2%80%99%20unwavering%20support%20of%20my%20dreams.%20However%2C%20upon%20reflection%2C%20it%20becomes%20evident%20that%20it%20was%20societal%20norms%20that%20once%20impeded%20the%20progress%20of%20women%20like%20me.%20With%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20I%20never%20let%20the%20societal%20pressure%20win.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20similar%20lines%2C%20Sonali%20also%20recalled%20how%20being%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20highly%20male-dominated%20profession%20played%20out%20for%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20mental%20well-being%2C%20workplaces%20in%20Assam%20and%20North%20Easter%20India%20are%20far%20better%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20Women%20are%20free%20to%20dress%2C%20talk%20and%20behave%20in%20any%20manner%20they%20wish%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20the%20job%20was%20male-dominated%2C%20the%20workplace%20often%20lacked%20hygiene%20requirements%20for%20a%20woman%20worker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20comfortably%20was%20very%20hard%20to%20come%20by%20back%20in%20those%20days.%20There%20was%20always%20a%20lack%20of%20hygiene%2C%20However%2C%20things%20have%20become%20much%20better%20with%20more%20women%20joining%20the%20workforce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20she%20fared%20as%20the%20only%20woman%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20gender%20discrimination%20in%20the%20field%2C%20Ghosh%20recalls%20a%20time%20when%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20young%20ACF%20(Assistant%20Conservator%20of%20Forest)%20and%20was%20the%20only%20woman%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20around%20me%20would%20take%20some%20time%20to%20digest%20that%20a%20woman%20was%20in%20command.%20I%20would%20often%20hear%20gossip%20and%20chattering%20behind%20my%20back%2C%20but%20I%20never%20let%20it%20bother%20me.%20The%20one%20advice%20to%20all%20women%20out%20there%20in%20such%20a%20setting%20would%20be%20to%20develop%20a%20Rhino-like%20thick%20skin%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20general%2C%20the%20mindset%20of%20male%20bosses%20or%20colleagues%20is%20that%20women%20are%20meant%20for%20%E2%80%98softer%E2%80%99%20jobs.%20They%20thought%20that%20women%20could%20not%20or%20should%20not%20put%20in%20extra%20hours%20as%20they%20would%20need%20to%20tend%20to%20children%20and%20families.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20had%20to%20work%20extra%20hard%20to%20prove%20ourselves.%20But%20our%20assertiveness%20or%20proactive%20behaviour%20is%20often%20misconstrued%20as%20aggression%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sonali%20says%20that%20being%20in%20nature%20and%20among%20wildlife%20makes%20her%20job%20more%20fun%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330490%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESonali%20says%20that%20being%20in%20nature%20and%20among%20wildlife%20makes%20her%20job%20more%20fun.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Sonali%20says%2C%20she%20did%20not%20care%20about%20opinions%20and%20continued%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20work%2C%20keeping%20her%20work%20above%20everything%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMother%20to%20a%20young%20girl%2C%20she%20often%20had%20to%20spend%20months%20without%20her%20child%20away%20from%20home.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20cases%2C%20a%20strong%20family%20relationship%20is%20essential%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20workload%20could%20be%20such%20that%20I%20would%20end%20up%20neglecting%20even%20my%20health%20in%20many%20instances%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20family%20always%20came%20to%20her%20rescue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeing%20chased%20by%20rhinos%20to%20climbing%20trees%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20the%20field%20director%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%20she%20has%20held%20several%20other%20titles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20DFO%20(Divisional%20Forest%20Officer)%20at%20Kokrajhar%20where%20I%20managed%20a%20sanctuary%20and%20a%20highly%20endemic%20primate%20species%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Golden%20Langur%20or%20%3Cem%3ESonali%20Bandor.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%20My%20namesake%20and%20I%20have%20since%20then%20shared%20a%20special%20bond%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20lovingly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20of%20her%20favourite%20workplaces%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20fortunate%20to%20have%20served%20at%20Manas%20National%20Park%20with%20its%20sheer%20natural%20beauty%20and%20unique%20conservation%20and%20governance%20models.%20It%20taught%20me%20that%20there%20are%20many%20sides%20to%20a%20coin%20and%20one%20must%20appreciate%20history%20to%20become%20an%20effective%20administrator.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESonali%20also%20served%20a%20tenure%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Zoo%20in%20Delhi%20before%20she%20accepted%20the%20role%20at%20Kaziranga.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20Kaziranga%20her%20%3Cem%3EKarma%20Bhoomi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(land%20of%20action)%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshe%20fondly%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20career%20in%20the%20state%20at%20Kaziranga%20as%20a%20probationary%20trainee.%20At%20that%20time%20I%20was%2020%20years%20younger%20and%2020%20kg%20lighter!%20So%20when%20a%20rhino%20chased%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20courage%20and%20strength%20to%20climb%20a%20tree!%20I%20dread%20what%20will%20happen%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20a%20range%20of%20vital%20tasks%2C%20from%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%2C%20to%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20She%20also%20engages%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20delving%20into%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20exploring%20avenues%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215138%2Fsustainable-e-commerce-karnival-shopping-online-eco-friendly-homegrown-products-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Ghosh's%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20role%20demands%20precise%20monitoring%20of%20wildlife%20through%20scientific%20techniques%20and%20the%20careful%20management%20of%20tourism%20through%20the%20creation%20and%20execution%20of%20ecotourism%20initiatives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20her%20work%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20listener%20and%20understand%20how%20this%20famed%20protected%20area%20works.%20I%20have%20a%20great%20team%20with%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20forest%20frontline-to-area%20ratios%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20priority%20would%20be%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20protection%2C%20ensure%20and%20strengthen%20Rhinoceros%20and%20other%20flagship%20species%E2%80%99%20conservation.%20The%20second%20priority%20would%20be%20the%20utmost%20welfare%20of%20the%20forest%20frontline%20staff%20who%20serve%2024%C3%977%20in%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20conditions%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20has%20only%20been%2020%20days%20since%20Sonali%20assumed%20the%20new%20responsibility%2C%20she%20is%20quite%20geared%20up%20for%20the%20upcoming%20workload.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20great%20responsibility%20and%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20wait%20to%20give%20my%20best%20to%20nature%20and%20conserve%20the%20wildlife%20of%20the%20national%20park%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20women%20aspiring%20to%20be%20in%20the%20field%20of%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20in%20India%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20and%20young%20ladies%20who%20love%20outdoors%20and%20want%20to%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20must%20drop%20all%20their%20apprehensions%20and%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20There%20are%20several%20opportunities%20to%20explore%20and%20the%20sky%E2%80%99s%20the%20limit!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695303144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sonali%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20assumed%20the%20role%20as%20the%20field%20director%20of%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20on%201%20September%2C%202023%2C%20grew%20up%20having%20a%20close%20affinity%20to%20animals.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20completed%20her%20graduation%20in%20life%20sciences%2C%20her%20affinity%20had%20turned%20into%20a%20full%20blown%20passion.%20Being%20in%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20for%20decades%2C%20she%20recalls%20the%20hurdles%2C%20challenges%20and%20offers%20a%20glimpse%20into%20her%20life%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330465%2Ffirst-woman-director-of-kaziranga-national-park-struggles-challenges-stereotypes%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tripura%20IAS%20Officer%E2%80%99s%20Idea%20Is%20Preventing%20Girls%20From%20Leaving%20School%3B%20Stopped%2090%20Child%20Marriages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20on%20her%20way%20home%20from%20school%2C%2016-year-old%20Jyotsana%20Akhtar%20from%20Tripura%E2%80%99s%20Amzadnagar%20village%20heard%20people%20whispering%20while%20looking%20at%20her.%20When%20she%20overheard%20their%20conversation%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20aback%20to%20learn%20that%20her%20marriage%20was%20fixed!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20returned%20home%2C%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Emaa%3C%2Fem%3E%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20anything%20about%20the%20marriage.%20I%20found%20out%20from%20the%20villagers%20that%20I%20was%20to%20marry%20a%20man%20twice%20my%20age%20who%20had%20been%20divorced.%20It%20seemed%20like%20all%20my%20fears%20were%20soon%20to%20turn%20into%20reality%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20if%20I%20would%20ever%20return%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jyotsana%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20retaliated%20and%20refused%20to%20get%20married%20so%20early.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20study%20further%20and%20get%20a%20good%20job%2C%20if%20possible%20earn%20better%20than%20the%20man%20with%20whom%20my%20marriage%20was%20fixed.%20But%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20understand%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20week%2C%20she%20approached%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20school%20club%2C%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20teachers%20with%20her%20problem.%20Through%20them%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20intervened%20and%20prevented%20her%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20IAS%20officer%20has%20formed%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district%20to%20prevent%20child%20marriages.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20has%20formed%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district%20to%20prevent%20child%20marriages.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20officials%20informed%20my%20parents%20how%20early%20marriage%20would%20affect%20my%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%20and%20also%20told%20them%20that%20child%20marriage%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F108690%2Fchild-marriage-india-chronic-social-evil%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprohibited%20by%20the%20law%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20made%20them%20sign%20an%20affidavit%20promising%20they%20would%20not%20get%20me%20married%20till%20I%20turned%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Jyotsana%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20a%20student%20in%20Class%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20%E2%80%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20more%20about%20the%20initiative%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20battle%20against%20child%20marriages%20in%20Tripura%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBeti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20was%20started%20in%202020%20by%20the%20then%20collector%20Debapriya%20Bardhan%20to%20educate%20girls%20on%20adolescence%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20But%20the%20initiative%20turned%20dormant%20as%20schools%20shut%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257746%2Fias-hero-karnataka-ceo-zilla-parishad-prevents-child-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Saju%20Vaheed%20%E2%80%94%20a%202015%20batch%20IAS%20officer%20from%20Kerala%20%E2%80%94%20took%20over%20and%20joined%20as%20the%20Collector%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20and%20revived%20the%20initiative%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Saju%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20reviving%20this%20project%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20many%20female%20students%20of%20Classes%208%2C%209%2C%20and%2010%20were%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%20The%20education%20department%20informed%20me%20that%20it%20was%20because%20of%20child%20marriages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20si