onal%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years%20in%20Tripura%20%E2%80%94%20the%20third%20highest%20after%20West%20Bengal%20(41.6%20percent)%20and%20Bihar%20(40.8%20percent).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20a%20high%20percentage%20of%20underage%20girls%20are%20getting%20married%20in%20Tripura.%20Another%20issue%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20detect%20ongoing%20child%20marriages%20because%20they%20often%20involve%20local%20cooperation.%20Typically%2C%20we%20only%20find%20out%20about%20the%20marriage%20through%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20boyfriend%2C%20and%20sometimes%20we%E2%80%99re%20notified%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20making%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20prevent%20the%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20departments%20like%20health%20and%20social%20welfare%20would%20only%20get%20to%20know%20about%20these%20marriages%20when%20these%20young%20girls%20got%20pregnant%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20avail%20government%20schemes.%20Even%20though%20the%20departments%20knew%20it%20was%20illegal%20for%20these%20young%20girls%20to%20be%20married%2C%20they%20found%20themselves%20helpless%20when%20they%20found%20out%20about%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20early%20pregnancies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saju%20Vaheed%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20utilise%20Balika%20Manch%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2