lika%20Manch%20%3C%2Fem%3Erepresentatives%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Evisit%20the%20absentee%E2%80%99s%20house%20to%20enquire%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20learn%20that%20the%20family%20is%20forcing%20the%20girl%20to%20get%20married%2C%20they%20try%20to%20convince%20the%20family%20to%20get%20her%20back%20to%20school%20citing%20legal%20complications%20of%20the%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20formed%20WhatsApp%20groups%20of%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%2C%20women%20school%20management%20committees%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Childline%2C%20child%20welfare%20committees%2C%20and%20district-level%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%2C%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%20inform%20the%20group%20members%20about%20the%20case.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20parents%20are%20not%20convinced%2C%20then%20administrative%20support%20is%20sought.%20This%20is%20when%20our%20second%20layer%20of%20officials%20comes%20into%20the%20picture.%20It%20comprises%20a%20one-stop%20centre%20(where%20young%20girls%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20experts%20for%20counselling)%2C%20a%20district%20child%20protection%20unit%2C%20counsellors%2C%20psychologists%2C%20and%20legal%20practitioners%20who%20reach%20out%20to%20families%20to%20convince%20them.%20Most%20of%20the%20cases%20get%20resolved%20in%20the%20second%20layer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.