2023%2F09%2FTimelapse-Frame-12-1695044068-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mahendra%20Kumar%20Sharma%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pioneer%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20passed%20away%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20his%20loss%20was%20collectively%20mourned%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322281%2Fbengaluru-duo-uses-sports-to-help-rural-girls-study-in-school-sportz-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esports%20fraternity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20zeal%20was%20among%20the%20many%20qualities%20that%20were%20saluted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20Sharma%20who%20frequently%20organised%20softball%20tournaments%20for%20school%20and%20college-going%20girls%2C%20was%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20unfolding%20in%20England%20and%20Australia.%20Keen%20for%20Indian%20women%20to%20access%20these%20opportunities%2C%20he%20hatched%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%20the%20people%20of%20Lucknow%20woke%20up%20to%20clarion%20calls%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CKanyaon%20ki%20cricket%20hogi%2C%20zaroor%20aaiye%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Girls%20will%20be%20playing%20cricket%2C%20do%20come).%20The%20amplified%20voice%20belonged%20to%20none%20other%20than%20Sharma%2C%20who%20grouped%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321379%2Fmaitrayana-uses-netball-sports-to-educate-and-empower-young-girls%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterested%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20first%20association%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20in%20India.%20It%20was%20called%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20Association%20of%20India%20(WCAI)%20and%20was%20officially%20registered%20under%20the%20Societies%20Act%20of%20Lucknow%20in%201973.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20all-rounder%20in%20cricket%2C%20